(34, 24, 0, 'Resume: Backend Points', 'resume-backend-points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-php-%26-frameworks\">PHP &amp; Frameworks</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-implemented-security\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed and maintained web applications utilizing NodeJS, React, Angular, and JavaScript increasing<br>site reliability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Leveraged object-oriented programming (OOP) principles to create modular and maintainable<br>codebases, improving code quality and readability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented security measures to protect against common web vulnerabilities such as SQL injection<br>and cross-site scripting (XSS).<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Constructed RESTful APIs and integrated application with third-party services such as payment gateways(PayPal, Authorize.net, Stripe, square), document management tools, and CRMs.<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Integrated Apple Pay and Google Pay as alternative payment sources for customer portal, which resulting in a 20% increase in online&nbsp;transactions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built several fully functional e-commerce platforms, including features such as shopping carts, order<br>management, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li>Developed applications for city notaries, including features such as document&nbsp;management, appointment scheduling, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and implemented data models and database schemas to optimize data storage and retrieval.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Refactored an large PHP application into a service-oriented architecture, resulting in a 50% reduction in duplicate code, and a 25% improvement in overall performance and throughput.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a ‘Provider Portal’ to enable medical providers to check the status of their&nbsp;claims and their member’s eligibility. Estimated customer service call volume&nbsp;reduced by 50%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Architected product relationship, workflow and code separations for separation of&nbsp;concerns, isolated/easy deployment, with “Functional Specifications,” UML flow&nbsp;and sequence designs, with an API “services” back-end design.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked on a legacy app that provided a way to manage RFQs (Request for&nbsp;Quote). The app allows Bidders to see relevant jobs, provide a quote, and manage&nbsp;that workflow after winning the bid.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Restructured code to handle new user ID (IDM - Identity Management) change.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Design and developed role-based access of resources and SSO for authentication.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Setup monitoring site/API usage for analysis and future improvements.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a suite of tools to help owners manage their engine fleets through all their&nbsp;compliance needs, including maintenance, runtime logging, deviation records,&nbsp;performance testing, and document management.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed plugin which allows students to submit transportation request and administrator&nbsp;could view, manage and respond to request. Designed the user interface, handled client side as well as&nbsp;server-side validations.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed employment resource module which allows students to search, view and apply for jobs and&nbsp;employers to view job applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed Buyer module which is main part of the FHF and all the applicant can fill out the form.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed Dealer module to collect all information about FHF dealer.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built role-based authentication system using symfony security component.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Contact Management module to keep record of primary and secondary contact information of applicant,<br>dealer and co-applicant.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed module to automate printing and mailing post card using Stamps REST API.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed admin dashboard to manage contents, download section, photo gallery management system, online job application system, feedback system, online&nbsp;admission system, calendar and event management system, notification system.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed backend modules including product management, hierarchical category management,&nbsp;order management system.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Increased the company\'s net revenue for 3 years by 40% by automating all business processes,&nbsp;increasing the efficiency of issuing loans, reducing lending risks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Reduced the company\'s costs by 35% by choosing efficient technologies and methods for automating&nbsp;business processes.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a rating system for borrowers.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a system for analyzing and managing credit risks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a system for the formation and analysis of credit reports of borrowers in 3 credit bureaus.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Migrated legacy codebase to modern PHP standards and Tech Stack resulting in a 40% improvement in code<br>maintainability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed automated processes for collecting, organizing, and analyzing big data more than 500&nbsp;million.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Optimized web pages for maximum speed and scalability by leveraging caching techniques such as&nbsp;Memcached and Redis.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with cross-functional teams to design and implement RESTful APIs, enhancing data&nbsp;exchange efficiency within the architecture.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Engineered real-time data processing services, handling high volumes of data points per second.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Applied data structures and algorithms, enhancing the optimization and scalability of software<br>applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed multiple websites using Shopify Plus and React.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created a real-time communication platform using Node.js, Laravel, CodeIgniter, and Socket.io</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed and maintained credit monitoring software for the CSID platform using PHP and Symfony.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed a SaaS application (NFA Tools) for automatically filling out ATF forms using<br>PHP and CodeIgniter.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Integrated DocuSign for form signing and PHP 2D Barcode class for PDF417 barcode generation.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a headless e-commerce platform in PHP using a microservices architecture for WooCommerce and<br>WooCommerce Subscriptions, resulting in a 70% improvement in site performance and scalability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Engineered a high-efficiency photo upload module for customer ID verification using PHP, an internal structured<br>PHP framework, and JavaScript to improve accuracy, efficiency, and false positive identification by 60%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented custom APIs for a headless e-commerce system using native WordPress hooks, enabling seamless<br>integration with various frameworks (React, Express, Next.js) and third-party services.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Spearheaded the development of an innovative web application using PHP and MySQL, aimed at streamlining<br>the copay and deductible collection process for healthcare providers, enhancing financial efficiency by 40%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented advanced algorithms in PHP and Python to accurately calculate copays and deductibles,&nbsp;significantly reducing instances of under-collection and missed payments in medical practices by 32%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Architected high-performance RESTful API’s, and integrated real-time insurance verification features, minimizing<br>the occurrence of inaccurate insurance data and ensuring up-to-date patient coverage information.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed automated site creation tools and workflows integrating with Active Directory,&nbsp;enhancing