eved data.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created WCF Services responsible for communicating and providing real time data from integrated&nbsp;server to Client Application.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Involved in Database modeling, creating tables and in writing stored procedures using&nbsp;Oracle PL/SQL, actively used cursors, functions and calling procedures from one package to another&nbsp;package and created dynamic SQL statements in Oracle using&nbsp;PL/SQL and ADO.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Used LINQ for data retrieving, querying, storage and manipulation interface screens developed using&nbsp;ASP.net.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created a number of SQL Reports in large database with Design, Develop, and Build and publish the&nbsp;reports using Microsoft SQL Reporting Services.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-sql-%26-libraries\">SQL &amp; Libraries</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-with-sql-proc\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with SQL procedures, views, wrote complex sql queries including aggregate functions, sub&nbsp;queries, nested queries and joins.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and optimized PostgreSQL database schemas, reducing query response times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Assisted in restructuring database architecture and data retrieval using PHP and MySQL, reducing database<br>retrieval times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and implemented robust, high-traffic MySQL database architecture, and integrated Redis as an in-<br>memory data structure store for efficient caching, enhancing data processing speeds by 40%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Using complex SQL to create detailed reports to the specifications of the production teams.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Improved site speed by optimizing database queries and server configurations resulting in a 25%<br>improvement in load times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Improved database performance by optimizing queries and indexing resulting in a 20% reduction in query<br>time.</li>\r\n