(39, 24, 0, 'Resume: ChatGPT Prompts', 'resume-chatgpt-prompts', '<h3 id=\"bkmrk-prompts\">Prompts</h3>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-act-as-a-professiona\"><code>Act as a professional PHP Developer Resume Writer and draft me only 15 point bullet list of roles and responsibilities with \r\nfollowing duties and technologies that I performed for [Greenesol Power Systems Pvt Ltd]. Highlight all keywords(technologies)\r\n\r\nDuties:\r\n######\r\n\r\nConstructing User interfaces\r\nConstructing Webservices\r\nConstructing Database Models and writing complex sql queries\r\nWriting unit and integration testcases\r\nDeploying applications to cloud\r\nTeam player points\r\n\r\nTechnologies:\r\n############\r\n[PHP, Drupal, Wordpress, HTML, CSS, Javascript, jQuery, MySQL\r\nGit, Linux, Jenkins]\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-products-and-service\"><code>Products and Services offered by [Ovia Health]\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-give-me-only-plain-b\"><code>Give me only plain bullet list without explanation\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-include-following-bu\"><code>Include following business features in to above output and give me back only bullet points highlighting business features and keywords. \r\nInclude at least one business feature in to each resume point\r\n\r\nBusiness Features:\r\n##################\r\n[bullet point list of business features]\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-highlight-all-busine\"><code>Highlight all business features and keywords(technologies)\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-include-following-te\"><code>Include following terminology of [framework] and give me back only bullet points highlighting business features and keywords(technologies). \r\n\r\nTerminology:\r\n###########\r\n[terminology points]\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-remove-nesting-and-g\"><code>Remove nesting and give me plain list of bullet points and Highlight keywords and business features\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre id=\"bkmrk-add-metrics-to-above\"><code>Add metri