ve points. Metrics should demonstrate how features that I constructed helped business in terms of revenue and user visit\r\n\r\nAct as a resume writer and write professional summary for my resume considering following job description. I need only one paragraph with 5 sentences.\r\n\r\nJob Description:\r\n#################\r\n[job description from the website or email]\r\n\r\n', 3, '2024-01-19 16:00:44', '2024-02-04 19:42:46', 1, 8, 0, '', 4, 0, NULL, 1, '');
