(83, 20, 'Company Info', '<h1 id=\"bkmrk-reference--2\"><br></h1>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>GHRIAN TECHNOLOGIES:</strong></h1>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-1\">About the Company:</h1>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-tech-is-an-it\"><strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is an IT Company providing strategic and technology consulting in the field of Mobile, Web, and Software domains. We are primarily focused on designing and developing user-centered products and applications for clients. It is a team of individuals with diverse functional and technical expertise focused on solving business problems by developing customer-centric applications and enterprise business solutions. <strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is a place where one learns about the professionalism, ethics, values, and importance of client’s requirements and how to solve them efficiently using their product engineering and technology expertise.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-a-committed-team-of-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A committed team of professionals with different business vertical experiences, dedicated to identifying &amp; analyzing needs and suggesting the best tech solutions to make businesses run better. A team prepared to pull alongside our clients and put our years of experience, diverse backgrounds, education, and burning desire to simplify their business issues</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and\">Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</h2>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-technologies-\">Ghrian Technologies is dedicated to helping elite brands realize the transformative power of mobile experiences. By uncovering simple truths and pushing the boundaries of mobile innovation, the company aims to revolutionize customer interactions. With a global pursuit of authentic and innovative ideas, Ghrian Tech is committed to bringing these ideas to life through its <strong>strategic mobile,</strong> <strong>user interface, native app, web development, eCommerce, and software QA services.</strong></p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-the-company%27s-approa\">The company\'s approach involves thinking big, aligning strategies with partner needs, and creating engaging mobile experiences that prioritize user delight. From handcrafted native app development to responsive web design and eCommerce solutions, Ghrian Tech focuses on speed, customer satisfaction, and increased conversions. Additionally, the company provides a full suite of quality assurance services to ensure high-quality and optimized experiences that meet evolving QA requirements.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A\">REVENUE MODEL:</h2>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-technologies%27\">Ghrian Technologies\' revenue model is based on its comprehensive mobile strategy and development services. The company focuses on understanding the unique needs of its partners and aligning its teams to define effective strategies through rapid idea-storming workshops. By creating engaging mobile app experiences and prioritizing user delight, Ghrian Technologies ensures seamless and captivating applications.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-the-company%27s-commit\">The company\'s commitment to native app development and platform-specific optimization enhances the immersive nature of mobile experiences, contributing to increased user engagement and revenue generation. Additionally, Ghrian Technologies\' revenue model is strengthened by its dedication to quality assurance, ensuring the delivery of high-impact mobile solutions that drive revenue growth for its partners.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\"></p>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>MUTUAL OF OMAHA</strong></h1>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-2\">About the Company:</h1>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha-is-a\">Mutual of Omaha is a well-established insurance and financial services company with a rich history dating back to 1909. The company is known for providing a wide range of insurance products, including life insurance, disability insurance, long-term care insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha offers retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions. The company has a strong focus on customer satisfaction and is committed to helping individuals and families secure their financial futures through reliable and innovative insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-with-its-headquarter\">With its headquarters in Omaha, Nebraska, Mutual of Omaha has grown to become a prominent and trusted name in the insurance industry. The company\'s dedication to community involvement and corporate responsibility is evident through its support for various charitable organizations and initiatives aimed at improving the well-being of communities. Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to integrity, financial strength, and exceptional customer service has earned it a reputation as a reliable and customer-centric insurance provider, serving the diverse needs of individuals, families, and businesses across the United States.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and-1\">Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</h2>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-pr\">Mutual of Omaha\'s primary business is centered around providing <strong>insurance and financial services to individuals, families, and businesses</strong>. The company offers a comprehensive range of insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. In addition to insurance, Mutual of Omaha provides retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions to help its customers secure their financial future. The company\'s mission is to empower its customers to protect and enhance their financial well-being by offering reliable, innovative, and personalized insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-the-targeted-audienc\">The targeted audience for Mutual of Omaha includes individuals and families seeking insurance coverage for various life stages and needs. The company also caters to businesses looking for group insurance solutions and retirement planning services for their employees. Mutual of Omaha\'s mission is to serve the diverse needs of its customers by providing them with accessible, affordable, and high-quality insurance and financial products. The company is committed to delivering exceptional customer service and building lasting relationships with its clients, ensuring that they have the support and guidance they need to make informed decisions about their financial security.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-1\">REVENUE MODEL:</h2>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-re\">Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is based on a combination of revenue growth, solid earnings, and a strong policyholder surplus. Despite the challenges posed by the COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, the company reported impressive financial performance. With a GAAP pre-tax operating income of $742 million and revenues of $11.0 billion, Mutual of Omaha demonstrated its financial strength. The net income after taxes and realized investment gains was $698 million, reflecting the company\'s ability to navigate through difficult times.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-its-f\">In addition to its financial performance, Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to its policyholders is evident. The company\'s focus on providing outstanding service to its customers is reflected in its ability to provide COVID-related benefit payments to thousands of customers and their beneficiaries. This commitment, along with the dedication and contributions of the company\'s associates, has enabled Mutual of Omaha to overcome challenges and deliver for its policyholders.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-as-a-highly-rated%2C-f\">As a highly rated, Fortune 500 organization, Mutual of Omaha offers a variety of insurance and financial products for individuals, businesses, and groups throughout the United States. Being a mutual company owned by its policyholders, Mutual of Omaha is well-positioned for the future and committed to providing exceptional service to its customers.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-re-1\">Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is primarily based on the sale of insurance and financial products and the provision of related services. The company generates revenue through the premiums paid by policyholders for various insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha earns revenue from investment products and retirement planning services, such as annuities and mutual funds, which generate fees and commissions. The company also generates revenue from banking services, including deposits and lending products.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-direc\">In addition to direct sales, Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model includes investment income from the assets held by the company\'s investment portfolio. This includes income from fixed-income securities, equities, and other investment vehicles. The company also earns revenue from fees associated with its insurance and financial services, such as policy administration fees and asset management fees. Overall, Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is centered around providing comprehensive insurance and financial solutions to its customers while generating income from premiums, fees, commissions, and investment activities.</p>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-3e-company\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>3E Company</strong></h1>\r\n<h1 id=\"bkmrk-about-the-company%3A\">About the Company:</h1>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-glob\">3E Company is a global provider of intelligent compliance solutions, focusing on Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and product compliance expertise. With over 30 years of experience, they have earned the trust of leading companies worldwide. Their solutions empower clients to improve chemical and workplace safety, product safety, and supply chain transparency. 3E company is deeply committed to serving over 5,000 customers worldwide, including major chemical manufacturers, retailers, and pharmaceutical companies. They are dedicated to building a safer world and a more sustainable future through actionable intelligence and ESG performance improvement.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company%27s-dedicat\">3E Company\'s dedication to ensuring safety and sustainability, one product, one workplace, and one community at a time, has made it a trusted partner for organizations seeking to meet regulatory obligations while capturing market opportunities. Their expertise in EHS&amp;S and product compliance enables clients to accelerate the development and launch of products designed with safety from the start, ultimately contributing to a safer world and a more sustainable future.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and-2\">Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</h2>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-lead\">3E Company is a leading company based in Canton, Ohio. It is known for its expertise in environmental health and safety compliance and information management. The company provides a comprehensive suite of data and information services to help organizations comply with stringent regulatory requirements and ensure workplace safety. 3E Company\'s solutions include regulatory content, 24/7 emergency response services, regulatory reporting, and workplace safety training. The company\'s commitment to excellence and innovation has made it a trusted partner for businesses across various industries.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: var(--font-heading, var(--font-body)); font-size: 2.8275em; font-weight: 400;\">REVENUE MODEL:</span><br></p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-lead-1\">3E Company is a leading provider of environmental health and safety (EHS) compliance and information management services. The company offers a range of solutions to help businesses comply with regulations, manage risk, and improve workplace safety. 3E Company\'s revenue model is based on subscription services, consulting fees, and software licensing. The company provides its clients with access to a comprehensive database of regulatory content, as well as software tools for managing compliance and reporting. Additionally, 3E Company offers consulting services to help businesses develop and implement effective EHS management strategies. The company\'s revenue is generated through annual subscription fees for access to its regulatory content and software, as well as fees for consulting services and software licensing. This diversified revenue model allows 3E Company to provide value-added services to its clients while maintaining a steady stream of income.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk-3e%27s-estimated-annua\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 \">\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>3E\'s estimated annual revenue is currently $222.3M per year.</li>\r\n<li>3E\'s estimated revenue per employee is $294,000</li>\r\n<li>3E has 756 Employees.</li>\r\n<li>3E grew its employee count by 25% last year.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk--1\">\r\n<div class=\"col-7\"><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk--2\">\r\n<div class=\"col\"></div>\r\n</div>', '\r\nGHRIAN TECHNOLOGIES:\r\nAbout the Company:\r\nGhrian Tech is an IT Company providing strategic and technology consulting in the field of Mobile, Web, and Software domains. We are primarily focused on designing and developing user-centered products and applications for clients. It is a team of individuals with diverse functional and technical expertise focused on solving business problems by developing customer-centric applications and enterprise business solutions. Ghrian Tech is a place where one learns about the professionalism, ethics, values, and importance of client’s requirements and how to solve them efficiently using their product engineering and technology expertise.\r\nA committed team of professionals with different business vertical experiences, dedicated to identifying & analyzing needs and suggesting the best tech solutions to make businesses run better. A team prepared to pull alongside our clients and put our years of experience, diverse backgrounds, education, and burning desire to simplify their business issues\r\nCompany Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:\r\nGhrian Technologies is dedicated to helping elite brands realize the transformative power of mobile experiences. By uncovering simple truths and pushing the boundaries of mobile innovation, the company aims to revolutionize customer interactions. With a global pursuit of authentic and innovative ideas, Ghrian Tech is committed to bringing these ideas to life through its strategic mobile, user interface, native app, web development, eCommerce, and software QA services.\r\nThe company\'s approach involves thinking big, aligning strategies with partner needs, and creating engaging mobile experiences that prioritize user delight. From handcrafted native app development to responsive web design and eCommerce solutions, Ghrian Tech focuses on speed, customer satisfaction, and increased conversions. Additionally, the company provides a full suite of quality assurance services to ensure high-quality and optimized experiences that meet evolving QA requirements.\r\nREVENUE MODEL:\r\nGhrian Technologies\' revenue model is based on its comprehensive mobile strategy and development services. The company focuses on understanding the unique needs of its partners and aligning its teams to define effective strategies through rapid idea-storming workshops. By creating engaging mobile app experiences and prioritizing user delight, Ghrian Technologies ensures seamless and captivating applications.\r\nThe company\'s commitment to native app development and platform-specific optimization enhances the immersive nature of mobile experiences, contributing to increased user engagement and revenue generation. Additionally, Ghrian Technologies\' revenue model is strengthened by its dedication to quality assurance, ensuring the delivery of high-impact mobile solutions that drive revenue growth for its partners.\r\n\r\nMUTUAL OF OMAHA\r\nAbout the Company:\r\nMutual of Omaha is a well-established insurance and financial services company with a rich history dating back to 1909. The company is known for providing a wide range of insurance products, including life insurance, disability insurance, long-term care insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha offers retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions. The company has a strong focus on customer satisfaction and is committed to helping individuals and families secure their financial futures through reliable and innovative insurance and financial services.\r\nWith its headquarters in Omaha, Nebraska, Mutual of Omaha has grown to become a prominent and trusted name in the insurance industry. The company\'s dedication to community involvement and corporate responsibility is evident through its support for various charitable organizations and initiatives aimed at improving the well-being of communities. Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to integrity, financial strength, and exceptional customer service has earned it a reputation as a reliable and customer-centric insurance provider, serving the diverse needs of individuals, families, and businesses across the United States.\r\nCompany Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:\r\nMutual of Omaha\'s primary business is centered around providing insurance and financial services to individuals, families, and businesses. The company offers a comprehensive range of insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. In addition to insurance, Mutual of Omaha provides retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions to help its customers secure their financial future. The company\'s mission is to empower its customers to protect and enhance their financial well-being by offering reliable, innovative, and personalized insurance and financial services.\r\nThe targeted audience for Mutual of Omaha includes individuals and families seeking insurance coverage for various life stages and needs. The company also caters to businesses looking for group insurance solutions and retirement planning services for their employees. Mutual of Omaha\'s mission is to serve the diverse needs of its customers by providing them with accessible, affordable, and high-quality insurance and financial products. The company is committed to delivering exceptional customer service and building lasting relationships with its clients, ensuring that they have the support and guidance they need to make informed decisions about their financial security.\r\nREVENUE MODEL:\r\nMutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is based on a combination of revenue growth, solid earnings, and a strong policyholder surplus. Despite the challenges posed by the COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, the company reported impressive financial performance. With a GAAP pre-tax operating income of $742 million and revenues of $11.0 billion, Mutual of Omaha demonstrated its financial strength. The net income after taxes and realized investment gains was $698 million, reflecting the company\'s ability to navigate through difficult times.\r\nIn addition to its financial performance, Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to its policyholders is evident. The company\'s focus on providing outstanding service to its customers is reflected in its ability to provide COVID-related benefit payments to thousands of customers and their beneficiaries. This commitment, along with the dedication and contributions of the company\'s associates, has enabled Mutual of Omaha to overcome challenges and deliver for its policyholders.\r\nAs a highly rated, Fortune 500 organization, Mutual of Omaha offers a variety of insurance and financial products for individuals, businesses, and groups throughout the United States. Being a mutual company owned by its policyholders, Mutual of Omaha is well-positioned for the future and committed to providing exceptional service to its customers.\r\nMutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is primarily based on the sale of insurance and financial products and the provision of related services. The company generates revenue through the premiums paid by policyholders for various insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha earns revenue from investment products and retirement planning services, such as annuities and mutual funds, which generate fees and commissions. The company also generates revenue from banking services, including deposits and lending products.\r\nIn addition to direct sales, Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model includes investment income from the assets held by the company\'s investment portfolio. This includes income from fixed-income securities, equities, and other investment vehicles. The company also earns revenue from fees associated with its insurance and financial services, such as policy administration fees and asset management fees. Overall, Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is centered around providing comprehensive insurance and financial solutions to its customers while generating income from premiums, fees, commissions, and investment activities.\r\n3E Company\r\nAbout the Company:\r\n3E Company is a global provider of intelligent compliance solutions, focusing on Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and product compliance expertise. With over 30 years of experience, they have earned the trust of leading companies worldwide. Their solutions empower clients