(209, 34, 'Resume: Backend Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-php-%26-frameworks\">PHP &amp; Frameworks</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-implemented-security\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented security measures to protect against common web vulnerabilities such as SQL injection<br>and cross-site scripting (XSS).<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Constructed RESTful APIs and integrated application with third-party services such as&nbsp;payment gateways, document management tools, and CRMs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built several fully functional e-commerce platforms, including features such as shopping carts, order<br>management, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li>Developed applications for city notaries, including features such as document&nbsp;management, appointment scheduling, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and implemented data models and database schemas to optimize data storage and retrieval.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Refactored an large PHP application into a service-oriented architecture, resulting in a 50% reduction in duplicate code, and a 25% improvement in overall performance and throughput.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a ‘Provider Portal’ to enable medical providers to check the status of their&nbsp;claims and their member’s eligibility. Estimated customer service call volume&nbsp;reduced by 50%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Architected product relationship, workflow and code separations for separation of&nbsp;concerns, isolated/easy deployment, with “Functional Specifications,” UML flow&nbsp;and sequence designs, with an API “services” back-end design.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked on a legacy app that provided a way to manage RFQs (Request for&nbsp;Quote). The app allows Bidders to see relevant jobs, provide a quote, and manage&nbsp;that workflow after winning the bid.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Restructured code to handle new user ID (IDM - Identity Management) change.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Design and developed role-based access of resources and SSO for authentication.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Setup monitoring site/API usage for analysis and future improvements.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a suite of tools to help owners manage their engine fleets through all their&nbsp;compliance needs, including maintenance, runtime logging, deviation records,&nbsp;performance testing, and document management.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-sql-%26-libraries\">SQL &amp; Libraries</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-with-sql-proc\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with SQL procedures, views, wrote complex sql queries including aggregate functions, sub&nbsp;queries, nested queries and joins.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-production-support\">Production Support</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-responsible-for-main\">\r\n<li>Responsible for maintenance and debugging of existing applications(production support), fixing bugs, and improving functionality. Optimized database performance and implemented caching mechanisms to improve&nbsp;application performance and speed, ensuring smooth operation and customer&nbsp;satisfaction.</li>\r\n<li>Had an active part in resolving an average of 10 technical issues per week, resulting in a 25% increase in overall system efficiency.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-test-cases\">Test Cases</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-wrote-unit-test-and-\">\r\n<li>Wrote unit test and functional test using PHPUnit and Symfony WebTestCase component.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PHP & Frameworks\r\n\r\nImplemented security measures to protect against common web vulnerabilities such as SQL injectionand cross-site scripting (XSS).\r\nConstructed RESTful APIs and integrated application with third-party services such as payment gateways, document management tools, and CRMs.\r\nBuilt several fully functional e-commerce platforms, including features such as shopping carts, ordermanagement, and payment processing.\r\nDeveloped applications for city notaries, including features such as document management, appointment scheduling, and payment processing.\r\nDesigned and implemented data models and database schemas to optimize data storage and retrieval.\r\nRefactored an large PHP application into a service-oriented architecture, resulting in a 50% reduction in duplicate code, and a 25% improvement in overall performance and throughput.\r\nBuilt a ‘Provider Portal’ to enable medical providers to check the status of their claims and their member’s eligibility. Estimated customer service call volume reduced by 50%.\r\nArchitected product relationship, workflow and code separations for separation of concerns, isolated/easy deployment, with “Functional Specifications,” UML flow and sequence designs, with an API “services” back-end design.\r\nWorked on a legacy app that provided a way to manage RFQs (Request for Quote). The app allows Bidders to see relevant jobs, provide a quote, and manage that workflow after winning the bid.\r\nRestructured code to handle new user ID (IDM - Identity Management) change.\r\nDesign and developed role-based access of resources and SSO for authentication.\r\nSetup monitoring site/API usage for analysis and future improvements.\r\nBuilt a suite of tools to help owners manage their engine fleets through all their compliance needs, including maintenance, runtime logging, deviation records, performance testing, and document management.\r\n\r\nSQL & Libraries\r\n\r\nWorked with SQL procedures, views, wrote complex sql queries including aggregate functions, sub queries, nested queries and joins.\r\n\r\nProduction Support\r\n\r\nResponsible for maintenance and debugging of existing applications(production support), fixing bugs, and improving functionality. Optimized database performance and implemented caching mechanisms to improve application performance and speed, ensuring smooth operation and customer satisfaction.\r\nHad an active part in resolving an average of 10 technical issues per week, resulting in a 25% increase in overall system efficiency.\r\n\r\nTest Cases\r\n\r\nWrote unit test and functional test using PHPUnit and Symfony WebTestCase component.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 12:30:53', '2024-01-22 12:30:53', 'resume-backend-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 2),
(210, 35, 'Resume: FrontEnd Points', '<ul id=\"bkmrk-building-user-interf\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Building user interfaces and interactive web applications using Vue.js and Angular.js&nbsp;frameworks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed ajax datagrid with various functionalities like ajax pagination, retrieving,&nbsp;filtering, creating, modifying and deleting data with data in the form of JSON.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Generate interactive graphs using high charts library.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed responsive web templates, user friendly registration forms using HTML, CSS3,&nbsp;jQuery, bootstrap adhering to organization’s standards and browser compatibility.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n</ul>', '\r\nBuilding user interfaces and interactive web applications using Vue.js and Angular.js frameworks.\r\nDesigned and developed ajax datagrid with various functionalities like ajax pagination, retrieving, filtering, creating, modifying and deleting data with data in the form of JSON.\r\nGenerate interactive graphs using high charts library.\r\nDesigned and developed responsive web templates, user friendly registration forms using HTML, CSS3, jQuery, bootstrap adhering to organization’s standards and browser compatibility.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 12:31:04', '2024-01-22 12:31:04', 'resume-frontend-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 2),
(211, 37, 'Resume: Team Colloboration Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-general\">General</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-closely-with-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and develop<br>custom solutions to meet their needs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning new<br>skills.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">I ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-agile\">Agile</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-performed-efficient-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Performed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line&nbsp;with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features&nbsp;and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our&nbsp;customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'General\r\n\r\nWorked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and developcustom solutions to meet their needs.\r\nWorked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.\r\nCollaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning newskills.\r\nI ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.\r\n\r\nAgile\r\n\r\nPerformed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.\r\nWorked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 12:31:54', '2024-01-22 12:31:54', 'resume-team-colloboration-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 2),
