(228, 34, 'Resume: Backend Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-php-%26-frameworks\">PHP &amp; Frameworks</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-implemented-security\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed and maintained web applications utilizing NodeJS, React, Angular, and JavaScript increasing<br>site reliability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Leveraged object-oriented programming (OOP) principles to create modular and maintainable<br>codebases, improving code quality and readability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented security measures to protect against common web vulnerabilities such as SQL injection<br>and cross-site scripting (XSS).<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Constructed RESTful APIs and integrated application with third-party services such as payment gateways(PayPal, Authorize.net, Stripe, square), document management tools, and CRMs.<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Integrated Apple Pay and Google Pay as alternative payment sources for customer portal, which resulting in a 20% increase in online&nbsp;transactions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built several fully functional e-commerce platforms, including features such as shopping carts, order<br>management, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li>Developed applications for city notaries, including features such as document&nbsp;management, appointment scheduling, and payment processing.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and implemented data models and database schemas to optimize data storage and retrieval.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Refactored an large PHP application into a service-oriented architecture, resulting in a 50% reduction in duplicate code, and a 25% improvement in overall performance and throughput.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a ‘Provider Portal’ to enable medical providers to check the status of their&nbsp;claims and their member’s eligibility. Estimated customer service call volume&nbsp;reduced by 50%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Architected product relationship, workflow and code separations for separation of&nbsp;concerns, isolated/easy deployment, with “Functional Specifications,” UML flow&nbsp;and sequence designs, with an API “services” back-end design.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked on a legacy app that provided a way to manage RFQs (Request for&nbsp;Quote). The app allows Bidders to see relevant jobs, provide a quote, and manage&nbsp;that workflow after winning the bid.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Restructured code to handle new user ID (IDM - Identity Management) change.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Design and developed role-based access of resources and SSO for authentication.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Setup monitoring site/API usage for analysis and future improvements.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built a suite of tools to help owners manage their engine fleets through all their&nbsp;compliance needs, including maintenance, runtime logging, deviation records,&nbsp;performance testing, and document management.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed plugin which allows students to submit transportation request and administrator&nbsp;could view, manage and respond to request. Designed the user interface, handled client side as well as&nbsp;server-side validations.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed employment resource module which allows students to search, view and apply for jobs and&nbsp;employers to view job applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed Buyer module which is main part of the FHF and all the applicant can fill out the form.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed Dealer module to collect all information about FHF dealer.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built role-based authentication system using symfony security component.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Contact Management module to keep record of primary and secondary contact information of applicant,<br>dealer and co-applicant.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed module to automate printing and mailing post card using Stamps REST API.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed admin dashboard to manage contents, download section, photo gallery management system, online job application system, feedback system, online&nbsp;admission system, calendar and event management system, notification system.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed backend modules including product management, hierarchical category management,&nbsp;order management system.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Increased the company\'s net revenue for 3 years by 40% by automating all business processes,&nbsp;increasing the efficiency of issuing loans, reducing lending risks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Reduced the company\'s costs by 35% by choosing efficient technologies and methods for automating&nbsp;business processes.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a rating system for borrowers.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a system for analyzing and managing credit risks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a system for the formation and analysis of credit reports of borrowers in 3 credit bureaus.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Migrated legacy codebase to modern PHP standards and Tech Stack resulting in a 40% improvement in code<br>maintainability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed automated processes for collecting, organizing, and analyzing big data more than 500&nbsp;million.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Optimized web pages for maximum speed and scalability by leveraging caching techniques such as&nbsp;Memcached and Redis.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with cross-functional teams to design and implement RESTful APIs, enhancing data&nbsp;exchange efficiency within the architecture.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Engineered real-time data processing services, handling high volumes of data points per second.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Applied data structures and algorithms, enhancing the optimization and scalability of software<br>applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed multiple websites using Shopify Plus and React.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created a real-time communication platform using Node.js, Laravel, CodeIgniter, and Socket.io</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed and maintained credit monitoring software for the CSID platform using PHP and Symfony.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed a SaaS application (NFA Tools) for automatically filling out ATF forms using<br>PHP and CodeIgniter.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Integrated DocuSign for form signing and PHP 2D Barcode class for PDF417 barcode generation.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed a headless e-commerce platform in PHP using a microservices architecture for WooCommerce and<br>WooCommerce Subscriptions, resulting in a 70% improvement in site performance and scalability.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Engineered a high-efficiency photo upload module for customer ID verification using PHP, an internal structured<br>PHP framework, and JavaScript to improve accuracy, efficiency, and false positive identification by 60%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented custom APIs for a headless e-commerce system using native WordPress hooks, enabling seamless<br>integration with various frameworks (React, Express, Next.js) and third-party services.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Spearheaded the development of an innovative web application using PHP and MySQL, aimed at streamlining<br>the copay and deductible collection process for healthcare providers, enhancing financial efficiency by 40%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented advanced algorithms in PHP and Python to accurately calculate copays and deductibles,&nbsp;significantly reducing instances of under-collection and missed payments in medical practices by 32%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Architected high-performance RESTful API’s, and integrated real-time insurance verification features, minimizing<br>the occurrence of inaccurate insurance data and ensuring up-to-date patient coverage information.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-sql-%26-libraries\">SQL &amp; Libraries</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-with-sql-proc\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with SQL procedures, views, wrote complex sql queries including aggregate functions, sub&nbsp;queries, nested queries and joins.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and optimized PostgreSQL database schemas, reducing query response times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Assisted in restructuring database architecture and data retrieval using PHP and MySQL, reducing database<br>retrieval times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and implemented robust, high-traffic MySQL database architecture, and integrated Redis as an in-<br>memory data structure store for efficient caching, enhancing data processing speeds by 40%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Using complex SQL to create detailed reports to the specifications of the production teams.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Improved site speed by optimizing database queries and server configurations resulting in a 25%<br>improvement in load times.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Improved database performance by optimizing queries and indexing resulting in a 20% reduction in query<br>time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-production-support\">Production Support</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-responsible-for-main\">\r\n<li>Responsible for maintenance and debugging of existing applications(production support), fixing bugs, and improving functionality. Optimized database performance and implemented caching mechanisms to improve&nbsp;application performance and speed, ensuring smooth operation and customer&nbsp;satisfaction.</li>\r\n<li>Had an active part in resolving an average of 10 technical issues per week, resulting in a 25% increase in overall system efficiency.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Monitored performance of applications to identify issues or bottlenecks in order to improve their<br>efficiency. 3x performance increase.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Responsibility for the entire technical infrastructure of the company ensuring 99.9% uptime.</li>\r\n<li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-test-cases\">Test Cases</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-wrote-unit-test-and-\">\r\n<li>Wrote unit test and functional test using PHPUnit and Symfony WebTestCase component.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented automated testing frameworks for web applications to ensure quality control standards<br>were met.</li>\r\n<li>\r\n</ul>', 'PHP & Frameworks\r\n\r\nDeveloped and maintained web applications utilizing NodeJS, React, Angular, and JavaScript increasingsite reliability.\r\nLeveraged object-oriented programming (OOP) principles to create modular and maintainablecodebases, improving code quality and readability.\r\nImplemented security measures to protect against common web vulnerabilities such as SQL injectionand cross-site scripting (XSS).\r\nConstructed RESTful APIs and integrated application with third-party services such as payment gateways(PayPal, Authorize.net, Stripe, square), document management tools, and CRMs.\r\nIntegrated Apple Pay and Google Pay as alternative payment sources for customer portal, which resulting in a 20% increase in online transactions.\r\nBuilt several fully functional e-commerce platforms, including features such as shopping carts, ordermanagement, and payment processing.\r\nDeveloped applications for city notaries, including features such as document management, appointment scheduling, and payment processing.\r\nDesigned and implemented data models and database schemas to optimize data storage and retrieval.\r\nRefactored an large PHP application into a service-oriented architecture, resulting in a 50% reduction in duplicate code, and a 25% improvement in overall performance and throughput.\r\nBuilt a ‘Provider Portal’ to enable medical providers to check the status of their claims and their member’s eligibility. Estimated customer service call volume reduced by 50%.\r\nArchitected product relationship, workflow and code separations for separation of concerns, isolated/easy deployment, with “Functional Specifications,” UML flow and sequence designs, with an API “services” back-end design.\r\nWorked on a legacy app that provided a way to manage RFQs (Request for Quote). The app allows Bidders to see relevant jobs, provide a quote, and manage that workflow after winning the bid.\r\nRestructured code to handle new user ID (IDM - Identity Management) change.\r\nDesign and developed role-based access of resources and SSO for authentication.\r\nSetup monitoring site/API usage for analysis and future improvements.\r\nBuilt a suite of tools to help owners manage their engine fleets through all their compliance needs, including maintenance, runtime logging, deviation records, performance testing, and document management.\r\nDeveloped plugin which allows students to submit transportation request and administrator could view, manage and respond to request. Designed the user interface, handled client side as well as server-side validations.\r\nDeveloped employment resource module which allows students to search, view and apply for jobs and employers to view job applications.\r\nDeveloped Buyer module which is main part of the FHF and all the applicant can fill out the form.\r\nDeveloped Dealer module to collect all information about FHF dealer.\r\nBuilt role-based authentication system using symfony security component.\r\nContact Management module to keep record of primary and secondary contact information of applicant,dealer and co-applicant.\r\nDeveloped module to automate printing and mailing post card using Stamps REST API.\r\nDeveloped admin dashboard to manage contents, download section, photo gallery management system, online job application system, feedback system, online admission system, calendar and event management system, notification system.\r\nDeveloped backend modules including product management, hierarchical category management, order management system.\r\nIncreased the company\'s net revenue for 3 years by 40% by automating all business processes, increasing the efficiency of issuing loans, reducing lending risks.\r\nReduced the company\'s costs by 35% by choosing efficient technologies and methods for automating business processes.\r\nDeveloped a rating system for borrowers.\r\nDeveloped a system for analyzing and managing credit risks.\r\nDeveloped a system for the formation and analysis of credit reports of borrowers in 3 credit bureaus.\r\nMigrated legacy codebase to modern PHP standards and Tech Stack resulting in a 40% improvement in codemaintainability.\r\nDeveloped automated processes for collecting, organizing, and analyzing big data more than 500 million.\r\nOptimized web pages for maximum speed and scalability by leveraging caching techniques such as Memcached and Redis.\r\nCollaborated with cross-functional teams to design and implement RESTful APIs, enhancing data exchange efficiency within the architecture.\r\nEngineered real-time data processing services, handling high volumes of data points per second.\r\nApplied data structures and algorithms, enhancing the optimization and scalability of softwareapplications.\r\nDeveloped multiple websites using Shopify Plus and React.\r\nCreated a real-time communication platform using Node.js, Laravel, CodeIgniter, and Socket.io\r\nDeveloped and maintained credit monitoring software for the CSID platform using PHP and Symfony.\r\nDesigned and developed a SaaS application (NFA Tools) for automatically filling out ATF forms usingPHP and CodeIgniter.\r\nIntegrated DocuSign for form signing and PHP 2D Barcode class for PDF417 barcode generation.\r\nDeveloped a headless e-commerce platform in PHP using a microservices architecture for WooCommerce andWooCommerce Subscriptions, resulting in a 70% improvement in site performance and scalability.\r\nEngineered a high-efficiency photo upload module for customer ID verification using PHP, an internal structuredPHP framework, and JavaScript to improve accuracy, efficiency, and false positive identification by 60%.\r\nImplemented custom APIs for a headless e-commerce system using native WordPress hooks, enabling seamlessintegration with various frameworks (React, Express, Next.js) and third-party services.\r\nSpearheaded the development of an innovative web application using PHP and MySQL, aimed at streamliningthe copay and deductible collection process for healthcare providers, enhancing financial efficiency by 40%.\r\nImplemented advanced algorithms in PHP and Python to accurately calculate copays and deductibles, significantly reducing instances of under-collection and missed payments in medical practices by 32%.\r\nArchitected high-performance RESTful API’s, and integrated real-time insurance verification features, minimizingthe occurrence of inaccurate insurance data and ensuring up-to-date patient coverage information.\r\n\r\nSQL & Libraries\r\n\r\nWorked with SQL procedures, views, wrote complex sql queries including aggregate functions, sub queries, nested queries and joins.\r\nDesigned and optimized PostgreSQL database schemas, reducing query response times.\r\nAssisted in restructuring database architecture and data retrieval using PHP and MySQL, reducing databaseretrieval times.\r\nDesigned and implemented robust, high-traffic MySQL database architecture, and integrated Redis as an in-memory data structure store for efficient caching, enhancing data processing speeds by 40%.\r\nUsing complex SQL to create detailed reports to the specifications of the production teams.\r\nImproved site speed by optimizing database queries and server configurations resulting in a 25%improvement in load times.\r\nImproved database performance by optimizing queries and indexing resulting in a 20% reduction in querytime.\r\n\r\nProduction Support\r\n\r\nResponsible for maintenance and debugging of existing applications(production support), fixing bugs, and improving functionality. Optimized database performance and implemented caching mechanisms to improve application performance and speed, ensuring smooth operation and customer satisfaction.\r\nHad an active part in resolving an average of 10 technical issues per week, resulting in a 25% increase in overall system efficiency.\r\nMonitored performance of applications to identify issues or bottlenecks in order to improve theirefficiency. 3x performance increase.\r\nResponsibility for the entire technical infrastructure of the company ensuring 99.9% uptime.\r\n\r\n\r\nTest Cases\r\n\r\nWrote unit test and functional test using PHPUnit and Symfony WebTestCase component.\r\nImplemented automated testing frameworks for web applications to ensure quality control standardswere met.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 14:19:12', '2024-01-22 14:19:12', 'resume-backend-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 3);
