(229, 35, 'Resume: FrontEnd Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-general\">General</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-building-user-interf\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Building user interfaces and interactive web applications using Vue.js and Angular.js frameworks.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed ajax datagrid with various functionalities like ajax pagination, retrieving,&nbsp;filtering, creating, modifying and deleting data with data in the form of JSON.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Generate interactive graphs using high charts library.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and developed responsive web templates, user friendly registration forms using HTML, CSS3,&nbsp;jQuery, bootstrap adhering to organization’s standards and browser compatibility.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed website search component which allows the user to search for materials in the library using full text search feature of MySQL.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designing email templates.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed frontend interfaces including search, filter functionality for products, cart and checkout&nbsp;management modules.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with designers to create visually appealing websites that are optimized for search&nbsp;engines.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Contributing to digital modernization efforts by working on the LEAF (Lite Electron Action<br>Framework) application, enabling employees to implement workflows and digital forms rapidly.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Pioneering the development of a file management version control system within LEAF, enhancing the<br>efficiency and collaboration of developers working on template files.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Led front-end development to ensure high-performance, rich, and user-friendly applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Complete front-end rebuild using pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (jQuery), improving load times by 70%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Built an online appointment scheduling software that allows customers to schedule appointments<br>and reservations with their favorite businesses.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Led efficient development of Custom Websites and Landing Pages, optimizing capture of leads,<br>generate sales, and raise brand awareness.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Pioneered the creation of the newest version of the Custom Administration Panel used by the company,<br>enabling clients to visualize captured data and integrating with their existing systems through defined<br>endpoints.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-spa\">SPA</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-created-high-perform\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n<p>Created high-performance customer-facing e-Commerce applications using React, Redux/Saga, React Hooks and React-Router</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented React JS for front-end development resulting in a 30% increase in user retention.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-testing\">Testing</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-performed-cross-brow\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Performed cross-browser compatibility testing to ensure websites functioned properly across different<br>browsers and devices.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented automated testing suites, such as Jest, for increased code coverage.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'General\r\n\r\nBuilding user interfaces and interactive web applications using Vue.js and Angular.js frameworks.\r\nDesigned and developed ajax datagrid with various functionalities like ajax pagination, retrieving, filtering, creating, modifying and deleting data with data in the form of JSON.\r\nGenerate interactive graphs using high charts library.\r\nDesigned and developed responsive web templates, user friendly registration forms using HTML, CSS3, jQuery, bootstrap adhering to organization’s standards and browser compatibility.\r\nDeveloped website search component which allows the user to search for materials in the library using full text search feature of MySQL.\r\nDesigning email templates.\r\nDeveloped frontend interfaces including search, filter functionality for products, cart and checkout management modules.\r\nCollaborated with designers to create visually appealing websites that are optimized for search engines.\r\nContributing to digital modernization efforts by working on the LEAF (Lite Electron ActionFramework) application, enabling employees to implement workflows and digital forms rapidly.\r\nPioneering the development of a file management version control system within LEAF, enhancing theefficiency and collaboration of developers working on template files.\r\nLed front-end development to ensure high-performance, rich, and user-friendly applications.\r\nComplete front-end rebuild using pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (jQuery), improving load times by 70%.\r\nBuilt an online appointment scheduling software that allows customers to schedule appointmentsand reservations with their favorite businesses.\r\nLed efficient development of Custom Websites and Landing Pages, optimizing capture of leads,generate sales, and raise brand awareness.\r\nPioneered the creation of the newest version of the Custom Administration Panel used by the company,enabling clients to visualize captured data and integrating with their existing systems through definedendpoints.\r\n\r\n\r\nSPA\r\n\r\n\r\nCreated high-performance customer-facing e-Commerce applications using React, Redux/Saga, React Hooks and React-Router\r\n\r\nImplemented React JS for front-end development resulting in a 30% increase in user retention.\r\n\r\nTesting\r\n\r\nPerformed cross-browser compatibility testing to ensure websites functioned properly across differentbrowsers and devices.\r\nImplemented automated testing suites, such as Jest, for increased code coverage.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 14:19:13', '2024-01-22 14:19:13', 'resume-frontend-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 3),
(230, 36, 'Resume: Deployment Points', '<ul id=\"bkmrk-enhanced-security-fo\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Enhanced security for login modules using SSL implementation and encryption techniques.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Deployed applications onto production servers using various technologies such as Amazon Web<br>Services or Heroku.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Deployed applications on Kubernetes clusters, utilizing Kubernetes YAML files to define deployment<br>configurations, pods, and services for efficient scaling and orchestration.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and deployed scalable, highly available, and fault-tolerant systems on AWS (EC2, RDS, S3, Route 53),<br>reducing downtime by 30% and improving user experience.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented AWS cloud solutions using EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, Auto Scaling, and Elastic Load Balancing<br>(ELB), enhancing system efficiency and reducing infrastructure costs by 25%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Managed AWS infrastructure and automated deployment processes resulting in a 50% reduction in<br>deployment time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Utilized DevOps tools like Jenkins, Ansible to streamline development processes and increase team productivity<br>resulting in a 30% increase in code deployments.</li>\r\n</ul>', '\r\nEnhanced security for login modules using SSL implementation and encryption techniques.\r\nDeployed applications onto production servers using various technologies such as Amazon WebServices or Heroku.\r\nDeployed applications on Kubernetes clusters, utilizing Kubernetes YAML files to define deploymentconfigurations, pods, and services for efficient scaling and orchestration.\r\nDesigned and deployed scalable, highly available, and fault-tolerant systems on AWS (EC2, RDS, S3, Route 53),reducing downtime by 30% and improving user experience.\r\nImplemented AWS cloud solutions using EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, Auto Scaling, and Elastic Load Balancing(ELB), enhancing system efficiency and reducing infrastructure costs by 25%.\r\nManaged AWS infrastructure and automated deployment processes resulting in a 50% reduction indeployment time.\r\nUtilized DevOps tools like Jenkins, Ansible to streamline development processes and increase team productivityresulting in a 30% increase in code deployments.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 14:19:15', '2024-01-22 14:19:15', 'resume-deployment-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 2),
(231, 37, 'Resume: Team Colloboration Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-general\">General</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-closely-with-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and develop<br>custom solutions to meet their needs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning new<br>skills.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">I ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Hired, trained and mentored 10 staff members.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created and maintained a technology roadmap to ensure alignment with organizational goals.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Helped lead a team of developers in designing, developing, testing, and deploying microservices and<br>web tier applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-agile\">Agile</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-performed-efficient-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Performed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line&nbsp;with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features&nbsp;and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our&nbsp;customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Utilized Agile and Scrum methodologies to lead cross-functional development teams, fostering collaboration,<br>delivering iterative software releases, and ensuring timely project completion.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'General\r\n\r\nWorked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and developcustom solutions to meet their needs.\r\nWorked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.\r\nCollaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning newskills.\r\nI ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.\r\nHired, trained and mentored 10 staff members.\r\nCreated and maintained a technology roadmap to ensure alignment with organizational goals.\r\nHelped lead a team of developers in designing, developing, testing, and deploying microservices andweb tier applications.\r\n\r\n\r\nAgile\r\n\r\nPerformed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.\r\nWorked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.\r\nUtilized Agile and Scrum methodologies to lead cross-functional development teams, fostering collaboration,delivering iterative software releases, and ensuring timely project completion.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-22 14:19:16', '2024-01-22 14:19:16', 'resume-team-colloboration-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 3),
