ext search feature of MySQL.\r\nDesigning email templates.\r\nDeveloped frontend interfaces including search, filter functionality for products, cart and checkout management modules.\r\nCollaborated with designers to create visually appealing websites that are optimized for search engines.\r\nContributing to digital modernization efforts by working on the LEAF (Lite Electron ActionFramework) application, enabling employees to implement workflows and digital forms rapidly.\r\nPioneering the development of a file management version control system within LEAF, enhancing theefficiency and collaboration of developers working on template files.\r\nLed front-end development to ensure high-performance, rich, and user-friendly applications.\r\nComplete front-end rebuild using pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (jQuery), improving load times by 70%.\r\nBuilt an online appointment scheduling software that allows customers to schedule appointmentsand reservations with their favorite businesses.\r\nLed efficient development of Custom Websites and Landing Pages, optimizing capture of leads,generate sales, and raise brand awareness.\r\nPioneered the creation of the newest version of the Custom Administration Panel used by the company,enabling clients to visualize captured data and integrating with their existing systems through definedendpoints.\r\n\r\n\r\nSPA\r\n\r\n\r\nCreated high-performance customer-facing e-Commerce applications using React, Redux/Saga, React Hooks and React-Router\r\n\r\nImplemented React JS for front-end development resulting in a 30% increase in user retention.\r\nBuilding interactive front-end applications using Reactjs.\r\n\r\nTesting\r\n\r\nPerformed cross-browser compatibility testing to ensure websites functioned properly across differentbrowsers and devices.\r\nImplemented automated testing suites, such as Jest, for increased code coverage.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-25 12:03:46', '2024-01-25 12:03:46', 'resume-frontend-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '',