(264, 36, 'Resume: Deployment Points', '<ul id=\"bkmrk-enhanced-security-fo\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Enhanced security for login modules using SSL implementation and encryption techniques.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Deployed applications onto production servers using various technologies such as Amazon Web<br>Services or Heroku.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Deployed applications on Kubernetes clusters, utilizing Kubernetes YAML files to define deployment<br>configurations, pods, and services for efficient scaling and orchestration.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Designed and deployed scalable, highly available, and fault-tolerant systems on AWS (EC2, RDS, S3, Route 53),<br>reducing downtime by 30% and improving user experience.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented AWS cloud solutions using EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, Auto Scaling, and Elastic Load Balancing<br>(ELB), enhancing system efficiency and reducing infrastructure costs by 25%.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Managed AWS infrastructure and automated deployment processes resulting in a 50% reduction in<br>deployment time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Utilized DevOps tools like Jenkins, Ansible to streamline development processes and increase team productivity<br>resulting in a 30% increase in code deployments.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Orchestrated the provisioning of Azure virtual machines and conducted seamless code deployments.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Migrated Web applications to AWS using Elastic Beanstalk for deployment and Route 53 for DNS<br>management.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Developed and maintained Azure App Services for streamlined&nbsp;operations.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Implemented Azure App Services for hosting and managing&nbsp;applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Managed Azure Blob Storage for efficient data storage solutions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">\r\n</ul>', '\r\nEnhanced security for login modules using SSL implementation and encryption techniques.\r\nDeployed applications onto production servers using various technologies such as Amazon WebServices or Heroku.\r\nDeployed applications on Kubernetes clusters, utilizing Kubernetes YAML files to define deploymentconfigurations, pods, and services for efficient scaling and orchestration.\r\nDesigned and deployed scalable, highly available, and fault-tolerant systems on AWS (EC2, RDS, S3, Route 53),reducing downtime by 30% and improving user experience.\r\nImplemented AWS cloud solutions using EC2, S3, RDS, CloudFront, Auto Scaling, and Elastic Load Balancing(ELB), enhancing system efficiency and reducing infrastructure costs by 25%.\r\nManaged AWS infrastructure and automated deployment processes resulting in a 50% reduction indeployment time.\r\nUtilized DevOps tools like Jenkins, Ansible to streamline development processes and increase team productivityresulting in a 30% increase in code deployments.\r\nOrchestrated the provisioning of Azure virtual machines and conducted seamless code deployments.\r\nMigrated Web applications to AWS using Elastic Beanstalk for deployment and Route 53 for DNSmanagement.\r\nDeveloped and maintained Azure App Services for streamlined operations.\r\nImplemented Azure App Services for hosting and managing applications.\r\nManaged Azure Blob Storage for efficient data storage solutions.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-01-25 12:03:48', '2024-01-25 12:03:48', 'resume-deployment-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 3),
(265, 37, 'Resume: Team Colloboration Points', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-general\">General</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-worked-closely-with-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and develop<br>custom solutions to meet their needs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning new<br>skills.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">I ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Hired, trained and mentored 10 staff members.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Created and maintained a technology roadmap to ensure alignment with organizational goals.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Helped lead a team of developers in designing, developing, testing, and deploying microservices and<br>web tier applications.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Collaborating with cross-functional teams for requirement&nbsp;analysis and feature implementation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-documentation\">Documentation</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-produced-comprehensi\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Produced comprehensive technical documents detailing the team\'s milestones, ensuring clarity and<br>knowledge transfer within the team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-mentor\">Mentor</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-acted-as-a-mentor-an\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Acted as a mentor and technical lead for junior developers, fostering a culture of continuous learning<br>and quality coding practices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-agile\">Agile</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-performed-efficient-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Performed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line&nbsp;with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Worked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features&nbsp;and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our&nbsp;customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Utilized Agile and Scrum methodologies to lead cross-functional development teams, fostering collaboration,<br>delivering iterative software releases, and ensuring timely project completion.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'General\r\n\r\nWorked closely with project managers and clients to understand their requirements and developcustom solutions to meet their needs.\r\nWorked closely with stakeholders to understand their data requirements and translate them into technical specifications.\r\nCollaborated with other developers and designers on projects, sharing knowledge and learning newskills.\r\nI ensured ongoing collaboration between users, developers, and QA teams throughout the SDLC to deliver high-quality software solutions.\r\nHired, trained and mentored 10 staff members.\r\nCreated and maintained a technology roadmap to ensure alignment with organizational goals.\r\nHelped lead a team of developers in designing, developing, testing, and deploying microservices andweb tier applications.\r\nCollaborating with cross-functional teams for requirement analysis and feature implementation.\r\n\r\nDocumentation\r\n\r\nProduced comprehensive technical documents detailing the team\'s milestones, ensuring clarity andknowledge transfer within the team.\r\n\r\nMentor\r\n\r\nActed as a mentor and technical lead for junior developers, fostering a culture of continuous learningand quality coding practices.\r\n\r\nAgile\r\n\r\nPerformed efficient delivery of code based on principles of Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Integration (CI/CD) to keep in line with Agile Software Methodology principles and SCRUM process.\r\nWorked with an agile/scrum process using JIRA to manage our product features and our weekly task management. We were able to shift priorities based on our customer\'s needs, creating amazingly fast cycles of feature delivery and feedback.\r\nUtilized Agile and Scrum methodologies to lead cross-functional development teams, fostering collaboration,delivering iterative software releases, and ensuring timely project completion.\r\n', 1, '2024-01-25 12:03:49', '2024-01-25 12:03:49', 'resume-team-colloboration-points', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 4),
