lude Metrics into Resume Points.\r\nOrder Points in the Resume in the following way:\r\n\r\nBackend\r\nFrontend\r\nDeployment\r\nTools\r\nTeam Collaboration\r\n\r\n\r\nUpdate Resume points according to Job Description(keyword match should be more than 80%)\r\nAdd References to the bottom part of Resume.\r\nAdd Professional Summary to the beginning of the resume(Should be changed according to job description to highlight skills needed for the job).\r\n', 1, '2024-01-25 12:30:07', '2024-01-25 12:30:07', 'resume-preparation-checklist', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', 'Initial publish', 1),
