ation</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">PHP, Laravel, Reactjs, CSS, Payment Integration, Design patterns, MySQL<br>PHPUnit, Jest<br>AWS<br>Agile, Support</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>GHRIAN TECHNOLOGIES</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About the Company:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-tech-is-an-it\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is an IT Company providing strategic and technology consulting in the field of Mobile, Web, and Software domains. We are primarily focused on designing and developing user-centered products and applications for clients. It is a team of individuals with diverse functional and technical expertise focused on solving business problems by developing customer-centric applications and enterprise business solutions. <strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is a place where one learns about the professionalism, ethics, values, and importance of client’s requirements and how to solve them efficiently using their product engineering and technology expertise.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-a-committed-team-of-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A committed team of professionals with different business vertical experiences, dedicated to identifying &amp; analyzing needs and suggesting the best tech solutions to make businesses run better. A team prepared to pull alongside our clients and put our years of experience, diverse backgrounds, education, and burning desire to simplify their business issues.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>REVENUE</strong> <strong>MODEL</strong>:</h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-technologies%27\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Source of revenue for Ghrian Technologies is providing IT services(web app, mobile app and desktop app) to clients from different industries according to their business needs.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>NATIONWIDE</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About</strong> <strong>the</strong> <strong>Company</strong>:</h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha-is-a\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha is a well-established insurance and financial services company with a rich history dating back to 1909. The company is known for providing a wide range of insurance products, including life insurance, disability insurance, long-term care insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha offers retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions. The company has a strong focus on customer satisfaction and is committed to helping individuals and families secure their financial futures through reliable and innovative insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-with-its-headquarter\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">With its headquarters in Omaha, Nebraska, Mutual of Omaha has grown to become a prominent and trusted name in the insurance industry. The company\'s dedication to community involvement and corporate responsibility is evident through its support for various charitable organizations and initiatives aimed at improving the well-being of communities. Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to integrity, financial strength, and exceptional customer service has earned it a reputation as a reliable and customer-centric insurance provider, serving the diverse needs of individuals, families, and businesses across the United States.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-pr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha\'s primary business is centered around providing <strong>insurance and financial services to individuals, families, and businesses</strong>. The company offers a comprehensive range of insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. In addition to insurance, Mutual of Omaha provides retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions to help its customers secure their financial future. The company\'s mission is to empower its customers to protect and enhance their financial well-being by offering reliable, innovative, and personalized insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-the-targeted-audienc\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The targeted audience for Mutual of Omaha includes individuals and families seeking insurance coverage for various life stages and needs. The company also caters to businesses looking for group insurance solutions and retirement planning services for their employees. Mutual of Omaha\'s mission is to serve the diverse needs of its customers by providing them with accessible, affordable, and high-quality insurance and financial products. The company is committed to delivering exceptional customer service and building lasting relationships with its clients, ensuring that they have the support and guidance they need to make informed decisions about their financial security.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>REVENUE MODEL:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-re\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is based on a combination of revenue growth, solid earnings, and a strong policyholder surplus. Despite the challenges posed by the COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, the company reported impressive financial performance. With a GAAP pre-tax operating income of $742 million and revenues of $11.0 billion, Mutual of Omaha demonstrated its financial strength. The net income after taxes and realized investment gains was $698 million, reflecting the company\'s ability to navigate through difficult times.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-its-f\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In addition to its financial performance, Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to its policyholders is evident. The company\'s focus on providing outstanding service to its customers is reflected in its ability to provide COVID-related benefit payments to thousands of customers and their beneficiaries. This commitment, along with the dedication and contributions of the company\'s associates, has enabled Mutual of Omaha to overcome challenges and deliver for its policyholders.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-as-a-highly-rated%2C-f\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a highly rated, Fortune 500 organization, Mutual of Omaha offers a variety of insurance and financial products for individuals, businesses, and groups throughout the United States. Being a mutual company owned by its policyholders, Mutual of Omaha is well-positioned for the future and committed to providing exceptional service to its customers.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-direc\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-3e-company\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>3E Company</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-about-the-company%3A\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About the Company:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-glob\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3E Company is a global provider of intelligent compliance solutions, focusing on Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and product compliance expertise. With over 30 years of experience, they have earned the trust of leading companies worldwide. Their solutions empower clients to improve chemical and workplace safety, product safety, and supply chain transparency. 3E company is deeply committed to serving over 5,000 customers worldwide, including