(385, 20, 'Company Info', '<table id=\"bkmrk-company-type-of-appl\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 430.734px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 29.7969px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 29.7969px;\"><strong>Company</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 29.7969px;\"><strong>Type of Application</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 29.7969px;\"><strong>Technologies Used</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">Ghrian Technologies Pvt Ltd <br>(Hyd, India)</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">Online ticket booking app</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">PHP, Symfony, jQuery, Bootstrap, CSS, Javascript,SOLID Principles, MySQL<br>Git,Linux, Jenkins, Analytics,Payment Integration<br>Waterfall<br></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">Greenesol Power Systems Pvt Ltd (Hyd, India)</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">CMS</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">PHP, Drupal, Wordpress, HTML, CSS, Javascript, jQuery, MySQL<br>Git, Linux, Jenkins<br><br></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 96.9844px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 96.9844px;\">Mint Mobile (Costa Mesa, CA)</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 96.9844px;\">CRM</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 96.9844px;\">PHP, Symfony, Drupal, Angular, Reactjs, Tailwind, CSS, Design Patterns, Postgres<br>PHPunit, Jasmine<br>Azure<br>Agile</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 63.3906px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 63.3906px;\">3E Company</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 63.3906px;\">Intranet Web Application&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 63.3906px;\">PHP, Laravel, Reactjs, Tailwind, CSS<br>Azure, Postgres<br>PHPUnit<br>Agile, Support</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">NationWide</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">Insurance Web Application</td>\r\n<td style=\"height: 80.1875px;\">PHP, Laravel, Reactjs, CSS, Payment Integration, Design patterns, MySQL<br>PHPUnit, Jest<br>AWS, Analytics,Payment Integration<br>Agile, Support</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>GHRIAN TECHNOLOGIES</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About the Company:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-tech-is-an-it\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is an IT Company providing strategic and technology consulting in the field of Mobile, Web, and Software domains. We are primarily focused on designing and developing user-centered products and applications for clients. It is a team of individuals with diverse functional and technical expertise focused on solving business problems by developing customer-centric applications and enterprise business solutions. <strong>Ghrian Tech</strong> is a place where one learns about the professionalism, ethics, values, and importance of client’s requirements and how to solve them efficiently using their product engineering and technology expertise.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-a-committed-team-of-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A committed team of professionals with different business vertical experiences, dedicated to identifying &amp; analyzing needs and suggesting the best tech solutions to make businesses run better. A team prepared to pull alongside our clients and put our years of experience, diverse backgrounds, education, and burning desire to simplify their business issues.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>REVENUE</strong> <strong>MODEL</strong>:</h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-ghrian-technologies%27\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Source of revenue for Ghrian Technologies is providing IT services(web app, mobile app and desktop app) to clients from different industries according to their business needs.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>NATIONWIDE</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-info%3A-2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About</strong> <strong>the</strong> <strong>Company</strong>:</h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha-is-a\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha is a well-established insurance and financial services company with a rich history dating back to 1909. The company is known for providing a wide range of insurance products, including life insurance, disability insurance, long-term care insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha offers retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions. The company has a strong focus on customer satisfaction and is committed to helping individuals and families secure their financial futures through reliable and innovative insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-with-its-headquarter\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">With its headquarters in Omaha, Nebraska, Mutual of Omaha has grown to become a prominent and trusted name in the insurance industry. The company\'s dedication to community involvement and corporate responsibility is evident through its support for various charitable organizations and initiatives aimed at improving the well-being of communities. Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to integrity, financial strength, and exceptional customer service has earned it a reputation as a reliable and customer-centric insurance provider, serving the diverse needs of individuals, families, and businesses across the United States.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-pr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha\'s primary business is centered around providing <strong>insurance and financial services to individuals, families, and businesses</strong>. The company offers a comprehensive range of insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. In addition to insurance, Mutual of Omaha provides retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions to help its customers secure their financial future. The company\'s mission is to empower its customers to protect and enhance their financial well-being by offering reliable, innovative, and personalized insurance and financial services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-the-targeted-audienc\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The targeted audience for Mutual of Omaha includes individuals and families seeking insurance coverage for various life stages and needs. The company also caters to businesses looking for group insurance solutions and retirement planning services for their employees. Mutual of Omaha\'s mission is to serve the diverse needs of its customers by providing them with accessible, affordable, and high-quality insurance and financial products. The company is committed to delivering exceptional customer service and building lasting relationships with its clients, ensuring that they have the support and guidance they need to make informed decisions about their financial security.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>REVENUE MODEL:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-mutual-of-omaha%27s-re\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is based on a combination of revenue growth, solid earnings, and a strong policyholder surplus. Despite the challenges posed by the COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, the company reported impressive financial performance. With a GAAP pre-tax operating income of $742 million and revenues of $11.0 billion, Mutual of Omaha demonstrated its financial strength. The net income after taxes and realized investment gains was $698 million, reflecting the company\'s ability to navigate through difficult times.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-its-f\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In addition to its financial performance, Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to its policyholders is evident. The company\'s focus on providing outstanding service to its customers is reflected in its ability to provide COVID-related benefit payments to thousands of customers and their beneficiaries. This commitment, along with the dedication and contributions of the company\'s associates, has enabled Mutual of Omaha to overcome challenges and deliver for its policyholders.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-as-a-highly-rated%2C-f\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a highly rated, Fortune 500 organization, Mutual of Omaha offers a variety of insurance and financial products for individuals, businesses, and groups throughout the United States. Being a mutual company owned by its policyholders, Mutual of Omaha is well-positioned for the future and committed to providing exceptional service to its customers.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-in-addition-to-direc\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-3e-company\" class=\"align-center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>3E Company</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-about-the-company%3A\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About the Company:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-glob\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3E Company is a global provider of intelligent compliance solutions, focusing on Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and product compliance expertise. With over 30 years of experience, they have earned the trust of leading companies worldwide. Their solutions empower clients to improve chemical and workplace safety, product safety, and supply chain transparency. 3E company is deeply committed to serving over 5,000 customers worldwide, including major chemical manufacturers, retailers, and pharmaceutical companies. They are dedicated to building a safer world and a more sustainable future through actionable intelligence and ESG performance improvement.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company%27s-dedicat\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3E Company\'s dedication to ensuring safety and sustainability, one product, one workplace, and one community at a time, has made it a trusted partner for organizations seeking to meet regulatory obligations while capturing market opportunities. Their expertise in EHS&amp;S and product compliance enables clients to accelerate the development and launch of products designed with safety from the start, ultimately contributing to a safer world and a more sustainable future.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-company-business-and-2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Company Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-lead\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3E Company is a leading company based in Canton, Ohio. It is known for its expertise in environmental health and safety compliance and information management. The company provides a comprehensive suite of data and information services to help organizations comply with stringent regulatory requirements and ensure workplace safety. 3E Company\'s solutions include regulatory content, 24/7 emergency response services, regulatory reporting, and workplace safety training. The company\'s commitment to excellence and innovation has made it a trusted partner for businesses across various industries.</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>REVENUE MODEL:</strong></h5>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-3e-company-is-a-lead-1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3E Company is a leading provider of environmental health and safety (EHS) compliance and information management services. The company offers a range of solutions to help businesses comply with regulations, manage risk, and improve workplace safety. 3E Company\'s revenue model is based on subscription services, consulting fees, and software licensing. The company provides its clients with access to a comprehensive database of regulatory content, as well as software tools for managing compliance and reporting. Additionally, 3E Company offers consulting services to help businesses develop and implement effective EHS management strategies. The company\'s revenue is generated through annual subscription fees for access to its regulatory content and software, as well as fees for consulting services and software licensing. This diversified revenue model allows 3E Company to provide value-added services to its clients while maintaining a steady stream of income.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk-3e%27s-estimated-annua\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 \">\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>3E\'s estimated annual revenue is currently $222.3M per year.</li>\r\n<li>3E\'s estimated revenue per employee is $294,000</li>\r\n<li>3E has 756 Employees.</li>\r\n<li>3E grew its employee count by 25% last year.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-chegg\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>Chegg</strong></h3>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-about-chegg%3A\"><strong>About Chegg:</strong></p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-chegg-is-an-educatio\">Chegg is an education technology company that offers a variety of services and products to support students in their academic journey. Here are key points about Chegg:</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-products-under-chegg\"><strong>Products Under Chegg:</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" id=\"bkmrk-textbook-solutions%3A-\">\r\n<div class=\"col-7\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Textbook Solutions:</strong> Chegg provides a vast database of step-by-step textbook solutions for a wide range of academic subjects, aiding students in understanding complex concepts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Study Resources:</strong> Chegg offers study resources such as practice problems, flashcards, and study guides to help students reinforce their learning and prepare for exams.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chegg Study Pack:</strong> A subscription-based service that bundles multiple Chegg services, including textbook solutions, study resources, and 24/7 homework help.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chegg Writing:</strong> A tool that assists students in improving their writing skills by providing grammar and plagiarism checking, citation assistance, and suggestions for improving writing style.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chegg Tutors:</strong> An online tutoring platform connecting students with expert tutors in various subjects for personalized assistance.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Chegg Math Solver:</strong> A tool that allows students to solve math problems step by step, providing explanations for each solution.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-revenue-model%3A-chegg\"><strong>Revenue Model:</strong> Chegg generates revenue through a subscription-based model and direct product sales. Students can subscribe to the Chegg Study Pack for access to multiple services, or they can purchase individual products such as textbooks, study resources, and tutoring services.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-software-features-us\"><strong>Software Features Used in Chegg:</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" id=\"bkmrk-web-interface%3A-chegg\">\r\n<div class=\"col-7\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Web Interface:</strong> Chegg\'s web interface is user-friendly, providing easy navigation for students to access various services and resources.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Mobile Applications:</strong> Chegg offers mobile applications for both iOS and Android platforms, allowing students to access study materials and services on the go.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Cloud-Based Services:</strong> Chegg utilizes cloud infrastructure to ensure scalability and reliability of its services, enabling seamless access for a large user base.</li>\r\n<li><strong>E-commerce Functionality:</strong> The platform incorporates e-commerce features for the purchase of physical textbooks and other study materials.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-business-terminology\"><strong>Business Terminology:</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" id=\"bkmrk-subscription-model%3A-\">\r\n<div class=\"col-7\">\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Subscription Model:</strong> Chegg employs a subscription-based revenue model, where users pay a recurring fee for access to a bundle of educational services.</li>\r\n<li><strong>User Engagement:</strong> The company focuses on strategies to enhance user engagement, ensuring that students actively utilize and benefit from the provided resources.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Monetization Strategies:</strong> Chegg employs various monetization strategies, including subscription fees, individual product sales, and partnerships with educational institutions.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Market Expansion:</strong> Chegg continually explores opportunities for market expansion, both in terms of geographical reach and diversification of services to meet evolving student needs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tech-Driven Learning:</strong> Embracing technology-driven learning, Chegg leverages software tools and platforms to deliver innovative solutions that complement traditional educational methods.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-by-combining-these-p\">By combining these products, revenue models, software features, and business terminology, Chegg has become a comprehensive and influential player in the education technology sector, providing valuable support to students worldwide</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"bkmrk-work-experience\"><strong>Work Experience</strong></h3>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-chegg---%5Bwork-period\"><strong>Chegg - [Work Period Here]</strong></p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-core-software-develo\"><em>Core Software Developer</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk--1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-7\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Developed user interfaces using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create intuitive and visually appealing experiences for students using Chegg\'s various products.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented React.js and Angular frameworks to enhance <strong>user interactions</strong> and optimize front-end performance.</li>\r\n<li>Constructed RESTful APIs to integrate third-party services and enhance the functionality of Chegg\'s platforms.</li>\r\n<li>Utilized PHP, Node.js, Laravel, Symfony, Express.js, and Sails.js to build scalable and efficient <strong>web services</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Designed and implemented robust database models to support the diverse range of Chegg products.</li>\r\n<li>Wrote complex SQL queries for MySQL, Postgres, SQL Server, Oracle, MongoDB, and Redis <strong>databases</strong> to ensure <strong>data integrity</strong> and optimize performance.</li>\r\n<li>Authored comprehensive unit and integration test cases using PHPunit, Codeception, Jest, and Jasmine.</li>\r\n<li>Ensured the reliability and stability of Chegg\'s applications through <strong>systematic testing methodologies</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Successfully <strong>deployed</strong> applications to <strong>cloud environments</strong> such as AWS, Azure, and Jenkins.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented efficient deployment processes to enhance application scalability, reliability, and availability.</li>\r\n<li>Actively participated in <strong>agile methodologies,</strong> contributing to sprint planning, stand-ups, and retrospectives.</li>\r\n<li>Engaged in <strong>direct interactions</strong> with business stakeholders, translating their requirements into technical solutions.</li>\r\n<li>Provided strong <strong>leadership</strong> within the development team, guiding and mentoring fellow developers.</li>\r\n<li>Facilitated knowledge sharing, code reviews, and best practices to ensure a high standard of software development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- notionvc: 75c9d37c-8e82-4f58-ad43-88c42e37818a --><br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" id=\"bkmrk--2\">\r\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div>\r\n</div>', '\r\n\r\n\r\nCompany\r\nType of Application\r\nTechnologies Used\r\n\r\n\r\nGhrian Technologies Pvt Ltd (Hyd, India)\r\nOnline ticket booking app\r\nPHP, Symfony, jQuery, Bootstrap, CSS, Javascript,SOLID Principles, MySQLGit,Linux, Jenkins, Analytics,Payment IntegrationWaterfall\r\n\r\n\r\nGreenesol Power Systems Pvt Ltd (Hyd, India)\r\nCMS\r\nPHP, Drupal, Wordpress, HTML, CSS, Javascript, jQuery, MySQLGit, Linux, Jenkins\r\n\r\n\r\nMint Mobile (Costa Mesa, CA)\r\nCRM\r\nPHP, Symfony, Drupal, Angular, Reactjs, Tailwind, CSS, Design Patterns, PostgresPHPunit, JasmineAzureAgile\r\n\r\n\r\n3E Company\r\nIntranet Web Application \r\nPHP, Laravel, Reactjs, Tailwind, CSSAzure, PostgresPHPUnitAgile, Support\r\n\r\n\r\nNationWide\r\nInsurance Web Application\r\nPHP, Laravel, Reactjs, CSS, Payment Integration, Design patterns, MySQLPHPUnit, JestAWS, Analytics,Payment IntegrationAgile, Support\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGHRIAN TECHNOLOGIES\r\nAbout the Company:\r\nGhrian Tech is an IT Company providing strategic and technology consulting in the field of Mobile, Web, and Software domains. We are primarily focused on designing and developing user-centered products and applications for clients. It is a team of individuals with diverse functional and technical expertise focused on solving business problems by developing customer-centric applications and enterprise business solutions. Ghrian Tech is a place where one learns about the professionalism, ethics, values, and importance of client’s requirements and how to solve them efficiently using their product engineering and technology expertise.\r\nA committed team of professionals with different business vertical experiences, dedicated to identifying & analyzing needs and suggesting the best tech solutions to make businesses run better. A team prepared to pull alongside our clients and put our years of experience, diverse backgrounds, education, and burning desire to simplify their business issues.\r\nREVENUE MODEL:\r\nSource of revenue for Ghrian Technologies is providing IT services(web app, mobile app and desktop app) to clients from different industries according to their business needs.\r\n\r\nNATIONWIDE\r\nAbout the Company:\r\nMutual of Omaha is a well-established insurance and financial services company with a rich history dating back to 1909. The company is known for providing a wide range of insurance products, including life insurance, disability insurance, long-term care insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. Additionally, Mutual of Omaha offers retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions. The company has a strong focus on customer satisfaction and is committed to helping individuals and families secure their financial futures through reliable and innovative insurance and financial services.\r\nWith its headquarters in Omaha, Nebraska, Mutual of Omaha has grown to become a prominent and trusted name in the insurance industry. The company\'s dedication to community involvement and corporate responsibility is evident through its support for various charitable organizations and initiatives aimed at improving the well-being of communities. Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to integrity, financial strength, and exceptional customer service has earned it a reputation as a reliable and customer-centric insurance provider, serving the diverse needs of individuals, families, and businesses across the United States.\r\nCompany Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:\r\nMutual of Omaha\'s primary business is centered around providing insurance and financial services to individuals, families, and businesses. The company offers a comprehensive range of insurance products, including life insurance, health insurance, long-term care insurance, disability insurance, and Medicare supplement insurance. In addition to insurance, Mutual of Omaha provides retirement planning services, investment products, and banking solutions to help its customers secure their financial future. The company\'s mission is to empower its customers to protect and enhance their financial well-being by offering reliable, innovative, and personalized insurance and financial services.\r\nThe targeted audience for Mutual of Omaha includes individuals and families seeking insurance coverage for various life stages and needs. The company also caters to businesses looking for group insurance solutions and retirement planning services for their employees. Mutual of Omaha\'s mission is to serve the diverse needs of its customers by providing them with accessible, affordable, and high-quality insurance and financial products. The company is committed to delivering exceptional customer service and building lasting relationships with its clients, ensuring that they have the support and guidance they need to make informed decisions about their financial security.\r\nREVENUE MODEL:\r\nMutual of Omaha\'s revenue model is based on a combination of revenue growth, solid earnings, and a strong policyholder surplus. Despite the challenges posed by the COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, the company reported impressive financial performance. With a GAAP pre-tax operating income of $742 million and revenues of $11.0 billion, Mutual of Omaha demonstrated its financial strength. The net income after taxes and realized investment gains was $698 million, reflecting the company\'s ability to navigate through difficult times.\r\nIn addition to its financial performance, Mutual of Omaha\'s commitment to its policyholders is evident. The company\'s focus on providing outstanding service to its customers is reflected in its ability to provide COVID-related benefit payments to thousands of customers and their beneficiaries. This commitment, along with the dedication and contributions of the company\'s associates, has enabled Mutual of Omaha to overcome challenges and deliver for its policyholders.\r\nAs a highly rated, Fortune 500 organization, Mutual of Omaha offers a variety of insurance and financial products for individuals, businesses, and groups throughout the United States. Being a mutual company owned by its policyholders, Mutual of Omaha is well-positioned for the future and committed to providing exceptional service to its customers.\r\n\r\n3E Company\r\nAbout the Company:\r\n3E Company is a global provider of intelligent compliance solutions, focusing on Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and product compliance expertise. With over 30 years of experience, they have earned the trust of leading companies worldwide. Their solutions empower clients to improve chemical and workplace safety, product safety, and supply chain transparency. 3E company is deeply committed to serving over 5,000 customers worldwide, including major chemical manufacturers, retailers, and pharmaceutical companies. They are dedicated to building a safer world and a more sustainable future through actionable intelligence and ESG performance improvement.\r\n3E Company\'s dedication to ensuring safety and sustainability, one product, one workplace, and one community at a time, has made it a trusted partner for organizations seeking to meet regulatory obligations while capturing market opportunities. Their expertise in EHS&S and product compliance enables clients to accelerate the development and launch of products designed with safety from the start, ultimately contributing to a safer world and a more sustainable future.\r\nCompany Business and Targeted Audience/Mission:\r\n3E Company is a leading company based in Canton, Ohio. It is known for its expertise in environmental health and safety compliance and information management. The company provides a comprehensive suite of data and information services to help organizations comply with stringent regulatory requirements and ensure workplace safety. 3E Company\'s solutions include regulatory content, 24/7 emergency response services, regulatory reporting, and workplace safety training. The company\'s commitment to excellence and innovation has made it a trusted partner for businesses across various industries.\r\nREVENUE MODEL:\r\n3E Company is a leading provider of environmental health and safety (EHS) compliance and information management services. The company offers a range of solutions to help businesses comply with regulations, manage risk, and improve workplace safety. 3E Company\'s revenue model is based on subscription services, consulting fees, and software licensing. The company provides its clients with access to a comprehensive database of regulatory content, as well as software tools for managing compliance and reporting. Additionally, 3E Company offers consulting services to help businesses develop and implement effective EHS management strategies. The company\'s revenue is generated through annual subscription fees for access to its regulatory content and software, as well as fees for consulting services and software licensing. This diversified revenue model allows 3E Company to provide value-added services to its clients while maintaining a steady stream of income.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3E\'s estimated annual revenue is currently $222.3M per year.\r\n3E\'s estimated revenue per employee is $294,000\r\n3E has 756 Employees.\r\n3E grew its employee count by 25% last year.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nChegg\r\nAbout Chegg:\r\nChegg is an education technology company that offers a variety of services and products to support students in their academic journey. Here are key points about Chegg:\r\nProducts Under Chegg:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTextbook Solutions: Chegg provides a vast database of step-by-step textbook solutions for a wide range of academic subjects, aiding students in understanding complex concepts.\r\nStudy Resources: Chegg offers study resources such as practice problems, flashcards, and study guides to help students reinforce their learning and prepare for exams.\r\nChegg Study Pack: A subscription-based service that bundles multiple Chegg services, including textbook solutions, study resources, and 24/7 homework help.\r\nChegg Writing: A tool that assists students in improving their writing skills by providing grammar and plagiarism checking, citation assistance, and suggestions for improving writing style.\r\nChegg Tutors: An online tutoring platform connecting students with expert tutors in various subjects for personalized assistance.\r\nChegg Math Solver: A tool that allows students to solve math problems step by step, providing explanations for each solution.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRevenue Model: Chegg generates revenue through a subscription-based model and direct product sales. Students can subscribe to the Chegg Study Pack for access to multiple services, or they can purchase individual products such as textbooks, study resources, and tutoring services.\r\nSoftware Features Used in Chegg:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWeb Interface: Chegg\'s web interface is user-friendly, providing easy navigation for students to access various services and resources.\r\nMobile Applications: Chegg offers mobile applications for both iOS and Android platforms, allowing students to access study materials and services on the go.\r\nCloud-Based Services: Chegg utilizes cloud infrastructure to ensure scalability and reliability of its services, enabling seamless access for a large user base.\r\nE-commerce Functionality: The platform incorporates e-commerce features for the purchase of physical textbooks and other study materials.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBusiness Terminology:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSubscription Model: Chegg employs a subscription-based revenue model, where users pay a recurring fee for access to a bundle of educational services.\r\nUser Engagement: The company focuses on strategies to enhance user engagement, ensuring that students actively utilize and benefit from the provided resources.\r\nMonetization Strategies: Chegg employs various monetization strategies, including subscription fees, individual product sales, and partnerships with educational institutions.\r\nMarket Expansion: Chegg continually explores opportunities for market expansion, both in terms of geographical reach and diversification of services to meet evolving student needs.\r\nTech-Driven Learning: Embracing technology-driven learning, Chegg leverages software tools and platforms to deliver innovative solutions that complement traditional educational methods.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBy combining these products, revenue models, software features, and business terminology, Chegg has become a comprehensive and influential player in the education technology sector, providing valuable support to students worldwide\r\nWork Experience\r\nChegg - [Work Period Here]\r\nCore Software Developer\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDeveloped user interfaces using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create intuitive and visually appealing experiences for students using Chegg\'s various products.\r\nImplemented React.js and Angular frameworks to enhance user interactions and optimize front-end performance.\r\nConstructed RESTful APIs to integrate third-party services and enhance the functionality of Chegg\'s platforms.\r\nUtilized PHP, Node.js, Laravel, Symfony, Express.js, and Sails.js to build scalable and efficient web services.\r\nDesigned and implemented robust database models to support the diverse range of Chegg products.\r\nWrote complex SQL queries for MySQL, Postgres, SQL Server, Oracle, MongoDB, and Redis databases to ensure data integrity and optimize performance.\r\nAuthored comprehensive unit and integration test cases using PHPunit, Codeception, Jest, and Jasmine.\r\nEnsured the reliability and stability of Chegg\'s applications through systematic testing methodologies.\r\nSuccessfully deployed applications to cloud environments such as AWS, Azure, and Jenkins.\r\nImplemented efficient deployment processes to enhance application scalability, reliability, and availability.\r\nActively participated in agile methodologies, contributing to sprint planning, stand-ups, and retrospectives.\r\nEngaged in direct interactions with business stakeholders, translating their requirements into technical solutions.\r\nProvided strong leadership within the development team, guiding and mentoring fellow developers.\r\nFacilitated knowledge sharing, code reviews, and best practices to ensure a high standard of software development.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-02-01 21:42:32', '2024-02-01 21:42:32', 'company-info', 'sai-krishna-srungavarapu', 'version', '', '', 21);
