(414, 4, 'Prerequisites', '<p id=\"bkmrk-this-document-will-g\" class=\"callout info\"><strong>This document will guide you to learn and operate tools required for marketing your profile.</strong></p>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-plane%28project-manage\" style=\"list-style-type: tasklist;\">\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Create Dedicated Marketing Email</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Create new Phone line(Google Voice) and configure voice mail.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Create Whatsapp Business account with Google Voice Number(This  will make sure that your mobile number is authentic)</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Resume Management should be done in Google Docs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Resume Preparation with clients and dates.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Certifications related to the technology you mentioned in Resume.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Cover Letter Preparation.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">LinkedIn Profile Preparation.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Create profile inside all <a href=\"https://docs.weintegral.com/books/marketing/page/job-applications-job-portal-list\">Job Portals</a>.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">GitHub Profile with Code Samples(back date your commits).</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Portfolio Website.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">3 References(<a href=\"https://mysudo.com/mysudo-plans/\">Phone and Email)</a>.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Learn scripted phone call conversation</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Learn basic tech topics mentioned in the resume.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Learn basics of AI (Prompts to generate Resume Points) to update your resume according to requirement.</li>\r\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input disabled type=\"checkbox\">Make yourself part of Company Async communication Tools (Slack, Whats App and email)<br></li>\r\n</ul>', 'This document will guide you to learn and operate tools required for marketing your profile.\r\n\r\nCreate Dedicated Marketing Email\r\nCreate new Phone line(Google Voice) and configure voice mail.\r\nCreate Whatsapp Business account with Google Voice Number(This  will make sure that your mobile number is authentic)\r\nResume Management should be done in Google Docs.\r\nResume Preparation with clients and dates.\r\nCertifications related to the technology you mentioned in Resume.\r\nCover Letter Preparation.\r\nLinkedIn Profile Preparation.\r\nCreate profile inside all Job Portals.\r\nGitHub Profile with Code Samples(back date your commits).\r\nPortfolio Website.\r\n3 References(Phone and Email).\r\nLearn scripted phone call conversation\r\nLearn basic tech topics mentioned in the resume.\r\nLearn basics of AI (Prompts to generate Resume Points) to update your resume according to requirement.\r\nMake yourself part of Company Async communication Tools (Slack, Whats App and email)\r\n', 1, '2024-02-04 19:39:27', '2024-02-04 19:39:27', 'prerequisites', 'marketing', 'version', '', 'System auto-update of internal links', 17),
