(421, 60, 'Resume: Preparation Checklist', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-checklist\">Checklist</h4>\r\n<ol id=\"bkmrk-start-resume-with-at\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Start Resume with ATS Friendly Resume Template.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Prepare Your Marketing story with Clients and years.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Document info about clients\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\">About Client Business</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">The application used in Business</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Business Terminology</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Revenue Model</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Latest Achievements.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Prepare your Resume with the following points(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">Current Job should be in present tense and previous jobs should be in past tense</span>)\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Backend</li>\r\n<li>Frontend</li>\r\n<li>Deployment</li>\r\n<li>Testing</li>\r\n<li>Tools</li>\r\n<li>Team Collaboration</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Include Business Terminology into Resume points</li>\r\n<li>Include Metrics into Resume Points.</li>\r\n<li>Order Points in the Resume in the following way:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Backend</li>\r\n<li>Frontend</li>\r\n<li>Deployment</li>\r\n<li>Tools</li>\r\n<li>Team Collaboration</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Update Resume points according to Job Description(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">keyword match should be more than 80%</span>)</li>\r\n<li>Add References to the bottom part of Resume.</li>\r\n<li>Add a Professional Summary to the beginning of the resume(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">Should be changed according to the job description to highlight skills needed for the job</span>).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-references\">References</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-how-to-prepare-resum\">\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://www.indeed.com/career-advice/resumes-cover-letters\">How to Prepare Resume and Cover Letter</a> - Indeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Checklist\r\n\r\nStart Resume with ATS Friendly Resume Template.\r\nPrepare Your Marketing story with Clients and years.\r\nDocument info about clients\r\n\r\nAbout Client Business\r\nThe application used in Business\r\nBusiness Terminology\r\nRevenue Model\r\nLatest Achievements.\r\n\r\n\r\nPrepare your Resume with the following points(Current Job should be in present tense and previous jobs should be in past tense)\r\n\r\nBackend\r\nFrontend\r\nDeployment\r\nTesting\r\nTools\r\nTeam Collaboration\r\n\r\n\r\nInclude Business Terminology into Resume points\r\nInclude Metrics into Resume Points.\r\nOrder Points in the Resume in the following way:\r\n\r\nBackend\r\nFrontend\r\nDeployment\r\nTools\r\nTeam Collaboration\r\n\r\n\r\nUpdate Resume points according to Job Description(keyword match should be more than 80%)\r\nAdd References to the bottom part of Resume.\r\nAdd a Professional Summary to the beginning of the resume(Should be changed according to the job description to highlight skills needed for the job).\r\n\r\nReferences\r\n\r\nHow to Prepare Resume and Cover Letter - Indeed\r\n\r\n ', 1, '2024-02-04 19:43:39', '2024-02-04 19:43:39', 'resume-preparation-checklist', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 5),
(423, 60, 'Resume: Preparation Checklist', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-checklist\">Checklist</h4>\r\n<ol id=\"bkmrk-start-resume-with-at\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Start Resume with ATS Friendly Resume Template.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Prepare Your Marketing story with Clients, years and technologies used.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Document info about clients\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"null\">About Client Business</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">The application used in Business</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Business Terminology</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Revenue Model</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Latest Achievements.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Prepare your Resume with the following points(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">Current Job should be in present tense and previous jobs should be in past tense</span>)\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Backend</li>\r\n<li>Frontend</li>\r\n<li>Deployment</li>\r\n<li>Testing</li>\r\n<li>Tools</li>\r\n<li>Team Collaboration</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Include Business Terminology into Resume points</li>\r\n<li>Hyperlink Core Technologies and Clients with their websites.</li>\r\n<li>Include Metrics into Resume Points.</li>\r\n<li>Order Points in the Resume in the following way:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Backend</li>\r\n<li>Frontend</li>\r\n<li>Deployment</li>\r\n<li>Tools</li>\r\n<li>Team Collaboration</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Update Resume points according to Job Description(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">keyword match should be more than 80%</span>)<br></li>\r\n<li>Add a Professional Summary to the beginning of the resume(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">Should be changed according to the job description to highlight skills needed for the job</span>).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-references\">References</h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-how-to-prepare-resum\">\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://www.indeed.com/career-advice/resumes-cover-letters\">How to Prepare Resume and Cover Letter</a> - Indeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0\"></p>', 'Checklist\r\n\r\nStart Resume with ATS Friendly Resume Template.\r\nPrepare Your Marketing story with Clients, years and technologies used.\r\nDocument info about clients\r\n\r\nAbout Client Business\r\nThe application used in Business\r\nBusiness Terminology\r\nRevenue Model\r\nLatest Achievements.\r\n\r\n\r\nPrepare your Resume with the following points(Current Job should be in present tense and previous jobs should be in past tense)\r\n\r\nBackend\r\nFrontend\r\nDeployment\r\nTesting\r\nTools\r\nTeam Collaboration\r\n\r\n\r\nInclude Business Terminology into Resume points\r\nHyperlink Core Technologies and Clients with their websites.\r\nInclude Metrics into Resume Points.\r\nOrder Points in the Resume in the following way:\r\n\r\nBackend\r\nFrontend\r\nDeployment\r\nTools\r\nTeam Collaboration\r\n\r\n\r\nUpdate Resume points according to Job Description(keyword match should be more than 80%)\r\nAdd a Professional Summary to the beginning of the resume(Should be changed according to the job description to highlight skills needed for the job).\r\n\r\nReferences\r\n\r\nHow to Prepare Resume and Cover Letter - Indeed\r\n\r\n', 1, '2024-02-04 19:52:53', '2024-02-04 19:52:53', 'resume-preparation-checklist', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 6),
(425, 13, 'Day to Day Activities', '<p id=\"bkmrk-this-document-contai\" class=\"callout info\"><strong>This document contains things that you have to do on daily basis respective to marketing your profile.</strong></p>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-targeted-resume-per-\">\r\n<li class=\"null\">Targeted Resume Per Requirement: Update Resume with <strong>Keywords</strong> in job description and bold them.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Create a copy from base resume. Name in this format (<strong>resume_yourname_vendor_client_date</strong>).</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Update <strong>Professional Summary and Job Titles</strong> according to your Job Description.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Track Progress of the Job Application: Update Submission sheet and Tracking software.<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Contact Management using Google Contacts: Save all vendor contact details for future.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Learn and Improvise Scripted Conversations on Phone.<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Use AI tool(Monica) forProfessional email replies.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Interview Prep.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Search Jobs in LinkedIn.</li>\r\n<li>Search Jobs in Job Portals.</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Follow up with vendors(Through email and phone).<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Remind References(People about the vendor calls).<br></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">Create calendar invites with interview schedules and send invites to assigned marketing person.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'This document contains things that you have to do on daily basis respective to marketing your profile.\r\n\r\nTargeted Resume Per Requirement: Update Resume with Keywords in job description and bold them.\r\nCreate a copy from base resume. Name in this format (resume_yourname_vendor_client_date).\r\nUpdate Professional Summary and Job Titles according to your Job Description.\r\nTrack Progress of the Job Application: Update Submission sheet and Tracking software.\r\nContact Management using Google Contacts: Save all vendor contact details for future. \r\nLearn and Improvise Scripted Conversations on Phone.\r\nUse AI tool(Monica) forProfessional email replies.\r\nInterview Prep.\r\nSearch Jobs in LinkedIn.\r\nSearch Jobs in Job Portals.\r\nFollow up with vendors(Through email and phone).\r\nRemind References(People about the vendor calls).\r\nCreate calendar invites with interview schedules and send invites to assigned marketing person.\r\n', 1, '2024-02-04 19:55:07', '2024-02-04 19:55:07', 'day-to-day-activities', 'marketing', 'version', '', '', 5),
(427, 26, 'Resume: Samples', '<ul id=\"bkmrk-php-developer-resume\">\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a title=\"PHP Developer Resume\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/14YFXOl0d6pr1e9l6RRmo4KrJbtzwx8M9?usp=drive_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PHP Developer Resume</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">FrontEnd Developer</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\">React Developer Resume</li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ciB4bDiWQVIXcNR16O8NhCSyrY3jA9vA?usp=drive_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">.NET Developer Resume</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1U6B2UAQWRiEIK4p8TUgOS_Eas0w6S1k5?usp=drive_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Node.js Developer Resume</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1P6czcbaLF8cJ2jQJqvgjqSAg9OSrUD38?usp=drive_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Java Developer Resume</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"null\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1TKh8CBKgYhn2QpxFB5WmtX6astoOsgWR?usp=drive_link\">SDET Automation Engineer Resume</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '\r\nPHP Developer Resume\r\nFrontEnd Developer\r\nReact Developer Resume\r\n.NET Developer Resume\r\nNode.js Developer Resume\r\nJava Developer Resume\r\nSDET Automation Engineer Resume\r\n', 1, '2024-02-05 00:38:03', '2024-02-05 00:38:03', 'resume-samples', 'resume-prep', 'version', '', '', 8),
