(603, 40, 'Scripted Conversations: Email', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-asking-reference-fro\">Asking Reference from People</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-refere\">Subject line: Reference Call Request for [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Bcolleague-name%5D%2C\">Hi [COLLEAGUE NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-am-in-the-process-\">I am in the process of applying for a [POSITION TITLE] position with [VENDOR NAME]. The hiring manager for [VENDOR NAME] might be calling you to do a reference check. Since we have worked together for [N NUMBER OF MONTHS], I am confident you will describe my skills and abilities.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-a-copy-of-my-current\">A copy of my current resume and job description is attached for your review. I am happy to discuss further or answer any outstanding questions you might have.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-in-advance\">Thank you in advance for your consideration.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-sincerely%2C%5Byour-name\">Sincerely,<br>[YOUR NAME]<br>P.S. I’ve attached my resume to this email for easy reference and here’s a link to the job description [JOB DESCRIPTION LINK].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-say-yes-to-recruiter\">Say YES to Recruiter</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-for-reachi\">Thank you for reaching out about this opportunity. It sounds like a great job and aligns with where I’d like to take my career. I’m eager to learn more.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-as-you-many-have-see\">As you many have seen on my resume, I have [NUMBER] years of experience in this field. I’ve been consistently committed to [SPECIFIC GOAL OR SKILLS]. In my current role at [CURRENT CLIENT], I recently [ACCOMPLISHMENTS RELATED TO NEW JOB].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-could-we-schedule-so\">Could we schedule some time to discuss this opportunity in more detail? I am interested to learn more about the role and share how my skills and experiences would benefit [NEW CLIENT].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i%E2%80%99m-available-to-tal\">I’m available to talk by phone on [every weekday between 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM CST]. I look forward to speaking with you.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-1\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-ask-recruiter-for-mo\">Ask Recruiter for more Info about requirement</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-1\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-for-reachi-1\">Thank you for reaching out about this opportunity. I’m grateful to be considered.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-currently%2C-i-enjoy-t\">Currently, I enjoy the work I’m doing for [CURRENT CLIENT]. However, this sounds like a great role, and I’m interested to learn more. Would it be possible for us to talk next week? I’m available for a phone conversation on [every weekday between 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM CST].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-moving-forward%2C-you-\">Moving forward, you can reach me directly here: s.gopibabu@hotmail.com or 508-530-2391.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-looking-forward-to-s\">Looking forward to speak with you!</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-2\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-ask-recruiter-to-con\">Ask Recruiter to Consider your resume for the position</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-%5Bjob-p\">Subject line: [JOB PORTAL NAME]-[JOB TITLE] - [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-2\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-my-name-is-%5Byour-nam\">My name is [YOUR NAME], and I am working as a [JOB TITLE] at [EMPLOYER NAME] . I am reaching out to you to communicate my interest in the [JOB TITLE]. I became aware of this by my search in [JOB PORTAL].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-am-confident-that-\">I am confident that my qualifications and experiences are a great match for this position. Specifically, I have [TWO HIGHLY RELEVANT ACCOMPLISHMENTS]. Attached to this email for your review are my cover letter and my resume.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-here-is-my-linkedin-\">Here is my LinkedIn profile(LINK). I’d love to meet and talk further about how we may work together.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-looking-forward-to-h\">Looking forward to hear from you.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-convey-recruiter-tha\">Convey Recruiter that you applied for the position</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-%5Bjob-t\">Subject line: [JOB TITLE] position - [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-3\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-recently-applied-f\">I recently applied for a job opening for the position of [POSITION NAME] on your [WEBSITE NAME]. The position fits perfectly with my experience in [SKILL 1, SKILL 2, SKILL 3]. You can learn more about me by viewing my LinkedIn Profile (LINK).</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-recently-followed-\">I recently followed your firm on Linkedin and appreciate the valuable resources you are providing for job seekers and interact with candidates. Also, I’m a fan of [COMMON INTEREST] too.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i%E2%80%99d-love-to-set-up-a\">I’d love to set up a time to schedule a call and talk about the position and my experience. I am avialable on [every weekday between 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM CST]. You can contact me at s.gopibabu@hotmail.com and 508-530-2391. I look forward to scheduling some time with you.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-4\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-convey-thanks-to-ven\">Convey thanks to vendor for meeting you</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-thank-\">Subject line: Thank you Note - [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name-%2F\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME / CLIENT NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-so-much-fo\">Thank you so much for meeting with me today.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-it-was-a-great-pleas\">It was a great pleasure to learn more about the team and position, and I’m very excited about the opportunity to join [CLIENT/VENDOR NAME] and help improve [APPLICATION NAME].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-especially-enjoyed\">I especially enjoyed talking to you about the determination to bring [APPLICATION NAME] to [SECTION OF AUDIENCE].</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-look-forward-to-he\">I look forward to hearing from you about the next steps in the hiring process, and please do not hesitate to contact me for any additional information.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-5\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-convey-client-that-y\">Convey Client that you applied for the position</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-interv\">Subject line: Interview Follow Up - [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-4\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-hope-all-is-well.-\">I hope all is well. I know how busy you probably are, but I recently applied to the [JOB TITLE] position and wanted to check in on your decision timeline.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i%E2%80%99m-excited-about-th\">I’m excited about the opportunity to join the team and contribute to the development of world-class products for your clients.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-you-can-also-learn-m\">You can also learn more about me and my experience and skills by viewing my LinkedIn Profile (LINK).</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-please-let-me-know%2C-\">Please let me know, if it would be helpful for me to provide any additional information as you move on to the next stage in the hiring process.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i-look-forward-to-he-1\">I look forward to hear from you.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-6\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-followup-after-inter\">Followup after Interview</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-subject-line%3A-interv-1\">Subject line: Interview Follow Up - [YOUR NAME]</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-5\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-just-wanted-to-thank\">Just wanted to thank you again for speaking with me earlier. I’m definitely going to follow up and reach out to [NAME OF PERSON] like you recommended. I’ll keep you in the loop, and of course, please let me know, if it would be helpful for me to provide any additional information as you move on to the next stage in the hiring process.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-7\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-say-no-to-job-offer\">Say NO to Job Offer</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-6\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thanks-for-thinking-\">Thanks for thinking of me for this role! I am currently exploring new opportunities, but would ideally like to find a position that would allow me to [PREFERRED JOB TITLE WITH TECHNOLOGIES]. It sounds like this particular role isn’t quite what I’m looking for, but do you happen to know of any other opportunities that may be a better fit? If so, I’d love to connect!</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-i%E2%80%99ve-attached-my-res\">I’ve attached my resume for your review, and can be reached directly at s.gopibabu@hotmail.com and 508-530-2391 moving forward.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-8\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-say-you-are-not-in-j\">Say you are not in Job Search&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-7\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-for-reachi-2\">Thank you for reaching out about this opportunity. I’m grateful to be considered.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-currently%2C-i-enjoy-t-1\">Currently, I enjoy the work I’m doing for [CURRENT CLIENT], and I’m not in the market for a new job. However, if I find myself pursuing a new job in the future, I’ll be in touch.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-%C2%A0-9\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-say-no-to-job-offer-1\">Say NO to Job Offer</h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-hi-%5Brecruiter-name%5D%2C-8\">Hi [RECRUITER NAME],</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-thank-you-again-for-\">Thank you again for the interview last week. It was great to meet the team. I enjoyed learning about the [JOB TITLE] position, and I appreciate your generous offer.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-while-this-position-\">While this position seems like a great opportunity, I’ve decided to pursue another role at another company. It’s been a pleasure getting to know you, and I hope that we cross paths in the future.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\"></p>', 'Asking Reference from People\r\nSubject line: Reference Call Request for [YOUR NAME]\r\nHi [COLLEAGUE NAME],\r\nI am in the process of applying for a [POSITION TITLE] position with [VENDOR NAME]. The hiring manager for [VENDOR NAME] might be calling you to do a reference check. Since we have worked together for [N NUMBER OF MONTHS], I am confident you will describe my skills and abilities.\r\nA copy of my current resume and job description is attached for your review. I am happy to discuss further or answer any outstanding questions you might have.\r\nThank you in advance for your consideration.\r\nSincerely,[YOUR NAME]P.S. I’ve attached my resume to this email for easy reference and here’s a link to the job description [JOB DESCRIPTION LINK].\r\n \r\nSay YES to Recruiter\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nThank you for reaching out about this opportunity. It sounds like a great job and aligns with where I’d like to take my career. I’m eager to learn more.\r\nAs you many have seen on my resume, I have [NUMBER] years of experience in this field. I’ve been consistently committed to [SPECIFIC GOAL OR SKILLS]. In my current role at [CURRENT CLIENT], I recently [ACCOMPLISHMENTS RELATED TO NEW JOB].\r\nCould we schedule some time to discuss this opportunity in more detail? I am interested to learn more about the role and share how my skills and experiences would benefit [NEW CLIENT].\r\nI’m available to talk by phone on [every weekday between 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM CST]. I look forward to speaking with you.\r\n \r\nAsk Recruiter for more Info about requirement\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nThank you for reaching out about this opportunity. I’m grateful to be considered.\r\nCurrently, I enjoy the work I’m doing for [CURRENT CLIENT]. However, this sounds like a great role, and I’m interested to learn more. Would it be possible for us to talk next week? I’m available for a phone conversation on [every weekday between 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM CST].\r\nMoving forward, you can reach me directly here: s.gopibabu@hotmail.com or 508-530-2391.\r\nLooking forward to speak with you