 [APPLICATION NAME] to [SECTION OF AUDIENCE].\r\nI look forward to hearing from you about the next steps in the hiring process, and please do not hesitate to contact me for any additional information.\r\n \r\nConvey Client that you applied for the position\r\nSubject line: Interview Follow Up - [YOUR NAME]\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nI hope all is well. I know how busy you probably are, but I recently applied to the [JOB TITLE] position and wanted to check in on your decision timeline.\r\nI’m excited about the opportunity to join the team and contribute to the development of world-class products for your clients.\r\nYou can also learn more about me and my experience and skills by viewing my LinkedIn Profile (LINK).\r\nPlease let me know, if it would be helpful for me to provide any additional information as you move on to the next stage in the hiring process.\r\nI look forward to hear from you.\r\n \r\nFollowup after Interview\r\nSubject line: Interview Follow Up - [YOUR NAME]\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nJust wanted to thank you again for speaking with me earlier. I’m definitely going to follow up and reach out to [NAME OF PERSON] like you recommended. I’ll keep you in the loop, and of course, please let me know, if it would be helpful for me to provide any additional information as you move on to the next stage in the hiring process.\r\n \r\nSay NO to Job Offer\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nThanks for thinking of me for this role! I am currently exploring new opportunities, but would ideally like to find a position that would allow me to [PREFERRED JOB TITLE WITH TECHNOLOGIES]. It sounds like this particular role isn’t quite what I’m looking for, but do you happen to know of any other opportunities that may be a better fit? If so, I’d love to connect!\r\nI’ve attached my resume for your review, and can be reached directly at s.gopibabu@hotmail.com and 508-530-2391 moving forward.\r\n \r\nSay you are not in Job Search \r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nThank you for reaching out about this opportunity. I’m grateful to be considered.\r\nCurrently, I enjoy the work I’m doing for [CURRENT CLIENT], and I’m not in the market for a new job. However, if I find myself pursuing a new job in the future, I’ll be in touch.\r\n \r\nSay NO to Job Offer\r\nHi [RECRUITER NAME],\r\nThank you again for the interview last week. It was great to meet the team. I enjoyed learning about the [JOB TITLE] position, and I appreciate your generous offer.\r\nWhile this position seems like a great opportunity, I’ve decided to pursue another role at another company. It’s been a pleasure getting to know you, and I hope that we cross paths in the future.\r\n', 1, '2024-05-06 20:13:57', '2024-05-06 20:13:58', 'scripted-conversations-email', 'marketing', 'version', '', '', 4);
